var book = {
	"name": "Matthew",
	"numChapters": 28,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>The record of the genealogy of Jesus the Messiah, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23146A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23146A\"></sup>the son of David, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23146B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23146B\"></sup>the son of Abraham:",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Abraham was the father of Isaac, Isaac the father of Jacob, and Jacob the father of Judah and his brothers.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Judah was the father of Perez and Zerah by Tamar, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23148C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23148C\"></sup>Perez was the father of Hezron, and Hezron the father of Ram.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Ram was the father of Amminadab, Amminadab the father of Nahshon, and Nahshon the father of Salmon.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Salmon was the father of Boaz by Rahab, Boaz was the father of Obed by Ruth, and Obed the father of Jesse.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Jesse was the father of David the king.David <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23151D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23151D\"></sup>was the father of Solomon by Bathsheba who had been the wife of Uriah.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Solomon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23152E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23152E\"></sup>was the father of Rehoboam, Rehoboam the father of Abijah, and Abijah the father of Asa.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Asa was the father of Jehoshaphat, Jehoshaphat the father of Joram, and Joram the father of Uzziah.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Uzziah was the father of Jotham, Jotham the father of Ahaz, and Ahaz the father of Hezekiah.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Hezekiah was the father of Manasseh, Manasseh the father of Amon, and Amon the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23155F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23155F\"></sup>father of Josiah.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Josiah became the father of Jeconiah and his brothers, at the time of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23156G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23156G\"></sup>deportation to Babylon.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>After the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23157H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23157H\"></sup>deportation to Babylon: Jeconiah became the father of Shealtiel, and Shealtiel the father of Zerubbabel.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Zerubbabel was the father of Abihud, Abihud the father of Eliakim, and Eliakim the father of Azor.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Azor was the father of Zadok, Zadok the father of Achim, and Achim the father of Eliud.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Eliud was the father of Eleazar, Eleazar the father of Matthan, and Matthan the father of Jacob.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Jacob was the father of Joseph the husband of Mary, by whom Jesus was born, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23161I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23161I\"></sup>who is called the Messiah.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>So all the generations from Abraham to David are fourteen generations; from David to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23162J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23162J\"></sup>deportation to Babylon, fourteen generations; and from the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23162K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23162K\"></sup>deportation to Babylon to the Messiah, fourteen generations.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Now the birth of Jesus Christ was as follows: when His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23163L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23163L\"></sup>mother Mary had been betrothed to Joseph, before they came together she was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23163M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23163M\"></sup>found to be with child by the Holy Spirit.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And Joseph her husband, being a righteous man and not wanting to disgrace her, planned <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23164N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23164N\"></sup>to send her away secretly.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But when he had considered this, behold, an angel of the Lord appeared to him in a dream, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23165O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23165O\"></sup>Joseph, son of David, do not be afraid to take Mary as your wife; for the Child who has been conceived in her is of the Holy Spirit.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>She will bear a Son; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23166P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23166P\"></sup>you shall call His name Jesus, for He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23166Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23166Q\"></sup>will save His people from their sins.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Now all this took place to fulfill what was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23167R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23167R\"></sup>spoken by the Lord through the prophet:",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23168S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23168S\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Behold, the virgin shall be with</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23168T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23168T\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">child and shall bear a Son, and they shall call His name</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Immanuel</span>,” which translated means, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23168U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23168U\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">God with us</span>.”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And Joseph awoke from his sleep and did as the angel of the Lord commanded him, and took <i>Mary</i> as his wife,",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>but kept her a virgin until she <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23170V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23170V\"></sup>gave birth to a Son; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23170W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23170W\"></sup>he called His name Jesus."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>Now after Jesus was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23171A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23171A\"></sup>born in Bethlehem of Judea in the days of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23171B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23171B\"></sup>Herod the king, magi from the east arrived in Jerusalem, saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Where is He who has been born <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23172C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23172C\"></sup>King of the Jews? For we saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23172D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23172D\"></sup>His star in the east and have come to worship Him.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>When Herod the king heard <i>this</i>, he was troubled, and all Jerusalem with him.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Gathering together all the chief priests and scribes of the people, he inquired of them where the Messiah was to be born.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>They said to him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23175E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23175E\"></sup>In Bethlehem of Judea; for this is what has been written by the prophet:",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23176F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23176F\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And you, Bethlehem, land of Judah</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Are by no means least among the leaders of Judah</span>;<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">For out of you shall come forth a Ruler</span><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Who will</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23176G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23176G\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">shepherd My people Israel</span>.’”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then Herod secretly called the magi and determined from them the exact time <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23177H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23177H\"></sup>the star appeared.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And he sent them to Bethlehem and said, “Go and search carefully for the Child; and when you have found <i>Him</i>, report to me, so that I too may come and worship Him.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>After hearing the king, they went their way; and the star, which they had seen in the east, went on before them until it came and stood over <i>the place</i> where the Child was.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>When they saw the star, they rejoiced exceedingly with great joy.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>After coming into the house they saw the Child with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23181I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23181I\"></sup>Mary His mother; and they fell to the ground and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23181J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23181J\"></sup>worshiped Him. Then, opening their treasures, they presented to Him gifts of gold, frankincense, and myrrh.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And having been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23182K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23182K\"></sup>warned <i>by God</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23182L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23182L\"></sup>in a dream not to return to Herod, the magi left for their own country by another way.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Now when they had gone, behold, an <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23183M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23183M\"></sup>angel of the Lord *<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23183N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23183N\"></sup>appeared to Joseph in a dream and said, “Get up! Take the Child and His mother and flee to Egypt, and remain there until I tell you; for Herod is going to search for the Child to destroy Him.”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>So Joseph got up and took the Child and His mother while it was still night, and left for Egypt.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>He remained there until the death of Herod. <i>This was</i> to fulfill what had been spoken by the Lord through the prophet: “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23185O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23185O\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Out of Egypt I called</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23185P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23185P\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">My Son</span>.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Then when Herod saw that he had been tricked by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23186Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23186Q\"></sup>the magi, he became very enraged, and sent and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23186R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23186R\"></sup>slew all the male children who were in Bethlehem and all its vicinity, from two years old and under, according to the time which he had determined from the magi.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Then what had been spoken through Jeremiah the prophet was fulfilled:",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23188S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23188S\"></sup>A <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">voice was heard in Ramah</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Weeping and great mourning</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Rachel weeping for her children</span>;<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And she refused to be comforted</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Because they were no more</span>.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>But when Herod died, behold, an angel of the Lord *<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23189T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23189T\"></sup>appeared in a dream to Joseph in Egypt, and said,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“Get up, take the Child and His mother, and go into the land of Israel; for those who sought the Child’s life are dead.”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>So Joseph got up, took the Child and His mother, and came into the land of Israel.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But when he heard that Archelaus was reigning over Judea in place of his father Herod, he was afraid to go there. Then after being <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23192U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23192U\"></sup>warned <i>by God</i> in a dream, he left for the regions of Galilee,",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>and came and lived in a city called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23193V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23193V\"></sup>Nazareth. <i>This was</i> to fulfill what was spoken through the prophets: “He shall be called a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23193W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23193W\"></sup>Nazarene.”"
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>Now <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23194A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23194A\"></sup>in those days <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23194B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23194B\"></sup>John the Baptist *came, preaching in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23194C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23194C\"></sup>wilderness of Judea, saying,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23195D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23195D\"></sup>Repent, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23195E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23195E\"></sup>the kingdom of heaven is at hand.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For this is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23196F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23196F\"></sup>one referred to by Isaiah the prophet when he said,“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23196G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23196G\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">The voice of one</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">crying in the wilderness</span>,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23196H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23196H\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Make ready the way of the Lord</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Make His paths straight</span>!’”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Now John himself had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23197I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23197I\"></sup>a garment of camel’s hair and a leather belt around his waist; and his food was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23197J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23197J\"></sup>locusts and wild honey.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then Jerusalem <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23198K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23198K\"></sup>was going out to him, and all Judea and all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23198L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23198L\"></sup>the district around the Jordan;",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and they were being <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23199M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23199M\"></sup>baptized by him in the Jordan River, as they confessed their sins.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But when he saw many of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23200N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23200N\"></sup>Pharisees and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23200O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23200O\"></sup>Sadducees coming for baptism, he said to them, “You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23200P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23200P\"></sup>brood of vipers, who warned you to flee from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23200Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23200Q\"></sup>the wrath to come?",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23201R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23201R\"></sup>Therefore bear fruit <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23201S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23201S\"></sup>in keeping with repentance;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>and do not suppose that you can say to yourselves, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23202T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23202T\"></sup>We have Abraham for our father’; for I say to you that from these stones God is able to raise up children to Abraham.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23203U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23203U\"></sup>axe is already laid at the root of the trees; therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23203V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23203V\"></sup>every tree that does not bear good fruit is cut down and thrown into the fire.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“As for me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23204W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23204W\"></sup>I baptize you with water for repentance, but He who is coming after me is mightier than I, and I am not fit to remove His sandals; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23204X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23204X\"></sup>He will baptize you with the Holy Spirit and fire.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23205Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23205Y\"></sup>winnowing fork is in His hand, and He will thoroughly clear His threshing floor; and He will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23205Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23205Z\"></sup>gather His wheat into the barn, but He will burn up the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23205AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23205AA\"></sup>chaff with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23205AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23205AB\"></sup>unquenchable fire.”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23206AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23206AC\"></sup>Then Jesus *arrived <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23206AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23206AD\"></sup>from Galilee at the Jordan <i>coming</i> to John, to be baptized by him.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But John tried to prevent Him, saying, “I have need to be baptized by You, and do You come to me?”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But Jesus answering said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Permit <i>it</i> at this time; for in this way it is fitting for us <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23208AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23208AE\"></sup>to fulfill all righteousness.”</span> Then he *permitted Him.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>After being baptized, Jesus came up immediately from the water; and behold, the heavens were opened, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23209AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23209AF\"></sup>he saw the Spirit of God descending as a dove <i>and</i> lighting on Him,",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>and behold, a voice out of the heavens said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23210AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23210AG\"></sup>This is My beloved Son, in whom I am well-pleased.”"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23211A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23211A\"></sup>Then Jesus was led up by the Spirit into the wilderness <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23211B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23211B\"></sup>to be tempted by the devil.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And after He had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23212C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23212C\"></sup>fasted forty days and forty nights, He then became hungry.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23213D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23213D\"></sup>the tempter came and said to Him, “If You are the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23213E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23213E\"></sup>Son of God, command that these stones become bread.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>But He answered and said, <span class=\"woj\">“It is written, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23214F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23214F\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Man shall not live on bread alone, but on every word that proceeds out of the mouth of God</span>.’”</span>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Then the devil *took Him into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23215G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23215G\"></sup>the holy city and had Him stand on the pinnacle of the temple,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and *said to Him, “If You are the Son of God, throw Yourself down; for it is written,‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23216H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23216H\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">He will command His angels concerning You</span>’;and‘<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">On</span> <i>their</i> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">hands they will bear You up</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">So that You will not strike Your foot against a stone</span>.’”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“On the other hand, it is written, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23217I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23217I\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You shall not put the Lord your God to the test</span>.’”</span>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23218J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23218J\"></sup>Again, the devil *took Him to a very high mountain and *showed Him all the kingdoms of the world and their glory;",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>and he said to Him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23219K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23219K\"></sup>All these things I will give You, if You fall down and worship me.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then Jesus *said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Go, Satan! For it is written, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23220L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23220L\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You shall worship the Lord your God, and</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">serve Him only</span>.’”</span>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Then the devil *left Him; and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23221M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23221M\"></sup>angels came and <i>began</i> to minister to Him.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Now when Jesus heard that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23222N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23222N\"></sup>John had been taken into custody, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23222O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23222O\"></sup>He withdrew into Galilee;",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>and leaving Nazareth, He came and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23223P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23223P\"></sup>settled in Capernaum, which is by the sea, in the region of Zebulun and Naphtali.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><i>This was</i> to fulfill what was spoken through Isaiah the prophet:",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23225Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23225Q\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">The land of Zebulun and the land of Naphtali</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">By the way of the sea, beyond the Jordan, Galilee of the</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Gentiles</span>—",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23226R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23226R\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">The people who were sitting in darkness saw a great Light</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And those who were sitting in the land and shadow of death</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Upon them a Light dawned</span>.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23227S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23227S\"></sup>From that time Jesus began to preach and say, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23227T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23227T\"></sup>Repent, for the kingdom of heaven is at hand.”</span>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23228U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23228U\"></sup>Now as Jesus was walking by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23228V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23228V\"></sup>the Sea of Galilee, He saw two brothers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23228W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23228W\"></sup>Simon who was called Peter, and Andrew his brother, casting a net into the sea; for they were fishermen.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>And He *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Follow Me, and I will make you fishers of men.”</span>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Immediately they left their nets and followed Him.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Going on from there He saw two other brothers, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23231X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23231X\"></sup>James the <i>son</i> of Zebedee, and John his brother, in the boat with Zebedee their father, mending their nets; and He called them.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Immediately they left the boat and their father, and followed Him.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Jesus was going <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23233Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23233Y\"></sup>throughout all Galilee, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23233Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23233Z\"></sup>teaching in their synagogues and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23233AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23233AA\"></sup>proclaiming the gospel of the kingdom, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23233AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23233AB\"></sup>healing every kind of disease and every kind of sickness among the people.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The news about Him spread <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23234AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23234AC\"></sup>throughout all Syria; and they brought to Him all who were ill, those suffering with various diseases and pains, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23234AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23234AD\"></sup>demoniacs, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23234AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23234AE\"></sup>epileptics, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23234AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23234AF\"></sup>paralytics; and He healed them.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Large crowds <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23235AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23235AG\"></sup>followed Him from Galilee and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23235AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23235AH\"></sup><i>the</i> Decapolis and Jerusalem and Judea and <i>from</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23235AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23235AI\"></sup>beyond the Jordan."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">5 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23236A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23236A\"></sup>When Jesus saw the crowds, He went up on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23236B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23236B\"></sup>the mountain; and after He sat down, His disciples came to Him.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23237C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23237C\"></sup>He opened His mouth and <i>began</i> to teach them, saying,",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23238D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23238D\"></sup>Blessed are the poor in spirit, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23238E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23238E\"></sup>theirs is the kingdom of heaven.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>“Blessed are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23239F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23239F\"></sup>those who mourn, for they shall be comforted.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“Blessed are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23240G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23240G\"></sup>the gentle, for they shall inherit the earth.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“Blessed are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23241H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23241H\"></sup>those who hunger and thirst for righteousness, for they shall be satisfied.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Blessed are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23242I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23242I\"></sup>the merciful, for they shall receive mercy.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“Blessed are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23243J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23243J\"></sup>the pure in heart, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23243K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23243K\"></sup>they shall see God.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“Blessed are the peacemakers, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23244L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23244L\"></sup>they shall be called sons of God.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“Blessed are those who have been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23245M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23245M\"></sup>persecuted for the sake of righteousness, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23245N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23245N\"></sup>theirs is the kingdom of heaven.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“Blessed are you when <i>people</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23246O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23246O\"></sup>insult you and persecute you, and falsely say all kinds of evil against you because of Me.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Rejoice and be glad, for your reward in heaven is great; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23247P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23247P\"></sup>in the same way they persecuted the prophets who were before you.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“You are the salt of the earth; but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23248Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23248Q\"></sup>if the salt has become tasteless, how can it be made salty <i>again</i>? It is no longer good for anything, except to be thrown out and trampled under foot by men.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“You are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23249R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23249R\"></sup>the light of the world. A city set on a hill cannot be hidden;</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23250S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23250S\"></sup>nor does <i>anyone</i> light a lamp and put it under a basket, but on the lampstand, and it gives light to all who are in the house.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Let your light shine before men in such a way that they may <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23251T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23251T\"></sup>see your good works, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23251U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23251U\"></sup>glorify your Father who is in heaven.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>“Do not think that I came to abolish the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23252V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23252V\"></sup>Law or the Prophets; I did not come to abolish but to fulfill.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For truly I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23253W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23253W\"></sup>until heaven and earth pass away, not the smallest letter or stroke shall pass from the Law until all is accomplished.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Whoever then annuls one of the least of these commandments, and teaches others <i>to do</i> the same, shall be called least <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23254X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23254X\"></sup>in the kingdom of heaven; but whoever keeps and teaches <i>them</i>, he shall be called great in the kingdom of heaven.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“For I say to you that unless your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23255Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23255Y\"></sup>righteousness surpasses <i>that</i> of the scribes and Pharisees, you will not enter the kingdom of heaven.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23256Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23256Z\"></sup>You have heard that the ancients were told, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23256AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23256AA\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You shall not commit murder</span>’ and ‘Whoever commits murder shall be liable to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23256AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23256AB\"></sup>the court.’</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But I say to you that everyone who is angry with his brother shall be guilty before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23257AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23257AC\"></sup>the court; and whoever says to his brother, ‘You good-for-nothing,’ shall be guilty before <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23257AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23257AD\"></sup>the supreme court; and whoever says, ‘You fool,’ shall be guilty <i>enough to go</i> into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23257AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23257AE\"></sup>fiery hell.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Therefore if you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23258AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23258AF\"></sup>presenting your offering at the altar, and there remember that your brother has something against you,</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>leave your offering there before the altar and go; first be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23259AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23259AG\"></sup>reconciled to your brother, and then come and present your offering.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23260AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23260AH\"></sup>Make friends quickly with your opponent at law while you are with him on the way, so that your opponent may not hand you over to the judge, and the judge to the officer, and you be thrown into prison.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Truly I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23261AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23261AI\"></sup>you will not come out of there until you have paid up the last cent.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23262AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23262AJ\"></sup>You have heard that it was said, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23262AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23262AK\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You shall not commit adultery</span>’;</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>but I say to you that everyone who looks at a woman <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23263AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23263AL\"></sup>with lust for her has already committed adultery with her in his heart.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23264AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23264AM\"></sup>If your right eye makes you stumble, tear it out and throw it from you; for it is better for you to lose one of the parts of your body, than for your whole body to be thrown into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23264AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23264AN\"></sup>hell.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23265AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23265AO\"></sup>If your right hand makes you stumble, cut it off and throw it from you; for it is better for you to lose one of the parts of your body, than for your whole body to go into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23265AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23265AP\"></sup>hell.</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“It was said, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23266AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23266AQ\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Whoever sends his wife away, let him give her a certificate of divorce</span>’;</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23267AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23267AR\"></sup>but I say to you that everyone who divorces his wife, except for <i>the</i> reason of unchastity, makes her commit adultery; and whoever marries a divorced woman commits adultery.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“Again, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23268AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23268AS\"></sup>you have heard that the ancients were told, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23268AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23268AT\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You shall not</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">make false vows, but shall fulfill your</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">vows to the Lord</span>.’</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>But I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23269AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23269AU\"></sup>make no oath at all, either by heaven, for it is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23269AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23269AV\"></sup>the throne of God,</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>or by the earth, for it is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23270AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23270AW\"></sup>footstool of His feet, or by Jerusalem, for it is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23270AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23270AX\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">the city of the great King</span>.</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Nor shall you make an oath by your head, for you cannot make one hair white or black.</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>But let your statement be, ‘Yes, yes’ <i>or</i> ‘No, no’; anything beyond these is of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23272AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23272AY\"></sup>evil.</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23273AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23273AZ\"></sup>You have heard that it was said, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23273BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23273BA\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">An eye for an eye, and a tooth for a tooth</span>.’</span>",
			"39": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>But I say to you, do not resist an evil person; but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23274BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23274BB\"></sup>whoever slaps you on your right cheek, turn the other to him also.</span>",
			"40": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>If anyone wants to sue you and take your shirt, let him have your coat also.</span>",
			"41": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>Whoever forces you to go one mile, go with him two.</span>",
			"42": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23277BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23277BC\"></sup>Give to him who asks of you, and do not turn away from him who wants to borrow from you.</span>",
			"43": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23278BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23278BD\"></sup>You have heard that it was said, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23278BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23278BE\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You shall love your neighbor</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23278BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23278BF\"></sup>and hate your enemy.’</span>",
			"44": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>But I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23279BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23279BG\"></sup>love your enemies and pray for those who persecute you,</span>",
			"45": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>so that you may be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23280BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23280BH\"></sup>sons of your Father who is in heaven; for He causes His sun to rise on <i>the</i> evil and <i>the</i> good, and sends rain on <i>the</i> righteous and <i>the</i> unrighteous.</span>",
			"46": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23281BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23281BI\"></sup>if you love those who love you, what reward do you have? Do not even the tax collectors do the same?</span>",
			"47": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>If you greet only your brothers, what more are you doing <i>than others</i>? Do not even the Gentiles do the same?</span>",
			"48": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23283BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23283BJ\"></sup>you are to be perfect, as your heavenly Father is perfect.</span>"
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<span class=\"woj\"><span class=\"chapternum\">6 </span>“Beware of practicing your righteousness before men <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23284A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23284A\"></sup>to be noticed by them; otherwise you have no reward with your Father who is in heaven.</span>",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“So when you give to the poor, do not sound a trumpet before you, as the hypocrites do in the synagogues and in the streets, so that they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23285B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23285B\"></sup>may be honored by men. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23285C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23285C\"></sup>Truly I say to you, they have their reward in full.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But when you give to the poor, do not let your left hand know what your right hand is doing,</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>so that your giving will be in secret; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23287D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23287D\"></sup>your Father who sees <i>what is done</i> in secret will reward you.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“When you pray, you are not to be like the hypocrites; for they love to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23288E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23288E\"></sup>stand and pray in the synagogues and on the street corners <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23288F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23288F\"></sup>so that they may be seen by men. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23288G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23288G\"></sup>Truly I say to you, they have their reward in full.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But you, when you pray, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23289H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23289H\"></sup>go into your inner room, close your door and pray to your Father who is in secret, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23289I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23289I\"></sup>your Father who sees <i>what is done</i> in secret will reward you.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“And when you are praying, do not use meaningless repetition as the Gentiles do, for they suppose that they will be heard for their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23290J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23290J\"></sup>many words.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>So do not be like them; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23291K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23291K\"></sup>your Father knows what you need before you ask Him.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23292L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23292L\"></sup>Pray, then, in this way:</span><span class=\"woj\">‘Our Father who is in heaven,</span><span class=\"woj\">Hallowed be Your name.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23293M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23293M\"></sup>Your kingdom come.</span><span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23293N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23293N\"></sup>Your will be done,</span><span class=\"woj\">On earth as it is in heaven.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23294O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23294O\"></sup>Give us this day our daily bread.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>‘And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23295P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23295P\"></sup>forgive us our debts, as we also have forgiven our debtors.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>‘And do not lead us into temptation, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23296Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23296Q\"></sup>deliver us from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23296R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23296R\"></sup>evil. </span>[<span class=\"woj\">For Yours is the kingdom and the power and the glory forever. Amen.’</span>]",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23297S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23297S\"></sup>For if you forgive others for their transgressions, your heavenly Father will also forgive you.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23298T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23298T\"></sup>if you do not forgive others, then your Father will not forgive your transgressions.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23299U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23299U\"></sup>Whenever you fast, do not put on a gloomy face as the hypocrites <i>do</i>, for they neglect their appearance so that they will be noticed by men when they are fasting. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23299V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23299V\"></sup>Truly I say to you, they have their reward in full.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But you, when you fast, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23300W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23300W\"></sup>anoint your head and wash your face</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>so that your fasting will not be noticed by men, but by your Father who is in secret; and your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23301X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23301X\"></sup>Father who sees <i>what is done</i> in secret will reward you.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23302Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23302Y\"></sup>Do not store up for yourselves treasures on earth, where moth and rust destroy, and where thieves break in and steal.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But store up for yourselves <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23303Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23303Z\"></sup>treasures in heaven, where neither moth nor rust destroys, and where thieves do not break in or steal;</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23304AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23304AA\"></sup>where your treasure is, there your heart will be also.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23305AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23305AB\"></sup>The eye is the lamp of the body; so then if your eye is clear, your whole body will be full of light.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But if <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23306AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23306AC\"></sup>your eye is bad, your whole body will be full of darkness. If then the light that is in you is darkness, how great is the darkness!</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23307AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23307AD\"></sup>No one can serve two masters; for either he will hate the one and love the other, or he will be devoted to one and despise the other. You cannot serve God and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23307AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23307AE\"></sup>wealth.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23308AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23308AF\"></sup>For this reason I say to you, do not be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23308AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23308AG\"></sup>worried about your life, <i>as to</i> what you will eat or what you will drink; nor for your body, <i>as to</i> what you will put on. Is not life more than food, and the body more than clothing?</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23309AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23309AH\"></sup>Look at the birds of the air, that they do not sow, nor reap nor gather into barns, and <i>yet</i> your heavenly Father feeds them. Are you not worth much more than they?</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And who of you by being <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23310AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23310AI\"></sup>worried can <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23310AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23310AJ\"></sup>add a <i>single</i> hour to his life?</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And why are you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23311AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23311AK\"></sup>worried about clothing? Observe how the lilies of the field grow; they do not toil nor do they spin,</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>yet I say to you that not even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23312AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23312AL\"></sup>Solomon in all his glory clothed himself like one of these.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>But if God so clothes the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23313AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23313AM\"></sup>grass of the field, which is <i>alive</i> today and tomorrow is thrown into the furnace, <i>will He</i> not much more <i>clothe</i> you? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23313AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23313AN\"></sup>You of little faith!</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Do not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23314AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23314AO\"></sup>worry then, saying, ‘What will we eat?’ or ‘What will we drink?’ or ‘What will we wear for clothing?’</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>For the Gentiles eagerly seek all these things; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23315AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23315AP\"></sup>your heavenly Father knows that you need all these things.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>But seek first His kingdom and His righteousness, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23316AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23316AQ\"></sup>all these things will be added to you.</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>“So do not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23317AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23317AR\"></sup>worry about tomorrow; for tomorrow will care for itself. Each day has enough trouble of its own.</span>"
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<span class=\"woj\"><span class=\"chapternum\">7 </span>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23318A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23318A\"></sup>Do not judge so that you will not be judged.</span>",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>For in the way you judge, you will be judged; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23319B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23319B\"></sup>by your standard of measure, it will be measured to you.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Why do you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23320C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23320C\"></sup>look at the speck that is in your brother’s eye, but do not notice the log that is in your own eye?</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23321D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23321D\"></sup>Or how can you say to your brother, ‘Let me take the speck out of your eye,’ and behold, the log is in your own eye?</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>You hypocrite, first take the log out of your own eye, and then you will see clearly to take the speck out of your brother’s eye.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23323E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23323E\"></sup>Do not give what is holy to dogs, and do not throw your pearls before swine, or they will trample them under their feet, and turn and tear you to pieces.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23324F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23324F\"></sup>Ask, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23324G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23324G\"></sup>it will be given to you; seek, and you will find; knock, and it will be opened to you.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For everyone who asks receives, and he who seeks finds, and to him who knocks it will be opened.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Or what man is there among you who, when his son asks for a loaf, will give him a stone?</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Or if he asks for a fish, he will not give him a snake, will he?</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>If you then, being evil, know how to give good gifts to your children, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23328H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23328H\"></sup>how much more will your Father who is in heaven give what is good to those who ask Him!</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“In everything, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23329I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23329I\"></sup>therefore, treat people the same way you want them to treat you, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23329J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23329J\"></sup>this is the Law and the Prophets.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23330K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23330K\"></sup>Enter through the narrow gate; for the gate is wide and the way is broad that leads to destruction, and there are many who enter through it.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For the gate is small and the way is narrow that leads to life, and there are few who find it.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Beware of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23332L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23332L\"></sup>false prophets, who come to you in sheep’s clothing, but inwardly are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23332M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23332M\"></sup>ravenous wolves.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>You will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23333N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23333N\"></sup>know them by their fruits. Grapes are not gathered from thorn <i>bushes</i> nor figs from thistles, are they?</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23334O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23334O\"></sup>every good tree bears good fruit, but the bad tree bears bad fruit.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>A good tree cannot produce bad fruit, nor can a bad tree produce good fruit.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23336P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23336P\"></sup>Every tree that does not bear good fruit is cut down and thrown into the fire.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>So then, you will know them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23337Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23337Q\"></sup>by their fruits.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23338R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23338R\"></sup>Not everyone who says to Me, ‘Lord, Lord,’ will enter the kingdom of heaven, but he who does the will of My Father who is in heaven <i>will enter</i>.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23339S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23339S\"></sup>Many will say to Me on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23339T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23339T\"></sup>that day, ‘Lord, Lord, did we not prophesy in Your name, and in Your name cast out demons, and in Your name perform many miracles?’</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And then I will declare to them, ‘I never knew you; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23340U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23340U\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">depart from Me, you who practice lawlessness</span>.’</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23341V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23341V\"></sup>everyone who hears these words of Mine and acts on them, may be compared to a wise man who built his house on the rock.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And the rain fell, and the floods came, and the winds blew and slammed against that house; and <i>yet</i> it did not fall, for it had been founded on the rock.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Everyone who hears these words of Mine and does not act on them, will be like a foolish man who built his house on the sand.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The rain fell, and the floods came, and the winds blew and slammed against that house; and it fell—and great was its fall.”</span>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23345W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23345W\"></sup>When Jesus had finished these words, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23345X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23345X\"></sup>the crowds were amazed at His teaching;",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>for He was teaching them as <i>one</i> having authority, and not as their scribes."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">8 </span>When Jesus came down from the mountain, large crowds followed Him.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23348A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23348A\"></sup>a leper came to Him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23348B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23348B\"></sup>bowed down before Him, and said, “Lord, if You are willing, You can make me clean.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Jesus stretched out His hand and touched him, saying, <span class=\"woj\">“I am willing; be cleansed.”</span> And immediately his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23349C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23349C\"></sup>leprosy was cleansed.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And Jesus *said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23350D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23350D\"></sup>See that you tell no one; but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23350E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23350E\"></sup>go, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23350F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23350F\"></sup>show yourself to the priest and present the offering that Moses commanded, as a testimony to them.”</span>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23351G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23351G\"></sup>when Jesus entered Capernaum, a centurion came to Him, imploring Him,",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and saying, “Lord, my servant is lying <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23352H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23352H\"></sup>paralyzed at home, fearfully tormented.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Jesus *said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“I will come and heal him.”</span>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But the centurion said, “Lord, I am not worthy for You to come under my roof, but just say the word, and my servant will be healed.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For I also am a man under <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23355I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23355I\"></sup>authority, with soldiers under me; and I say to this one, ‘Go!’ and he goes, and to another, ‘Come!’ and he comes, and to my slave, ‘Do this!’ and he does <i>it</i>.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Now when Jesus heard <i>this</i>, He marveled and said to those who were following, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly I say to you, I have not found such great faith with anyone in Israel.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>I say to you that many <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23357J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23357J\"></sup>will come from east and west, and recline <i>at the table</i> with Abraham, Isaac and Jacob in the kingdom of heaven;</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23358K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23358K\"></sup>the sons of the kingdom will be cast out into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23358L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23358L\"></sup>the outer darkness; in that place <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23358M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23358M\"></sup>there will be weeping and gnashing of teeth.”</span>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And Jesus said to the centurion, <span class=\"woj\">“Go; it shall be done for you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23359N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23359N\"></sup>as you have believed.”</span> And the servant was healed that <i>very</i> moment.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23360O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23360O\"></sup>When Jesus came into Peter’s home, He saw his mother-in-law lying sick in bed with a fever.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>He touched her hand, and the fever left her; and she got up and waited on Him.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>When evening came, they brought to Him many <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23362P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23362P\"></sup>who were demon-possessed; and He cast out the spirits with a word, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23362Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23362Q\"></sup>healed all who were ill.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><i>This was</i> to fulfill what was spoken through Isaiah the prophet: “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23363R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23363R\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">He Himself took our infirmities and</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">carried away our diseases</span>.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Now when Jesus saw a crowd around Him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23364S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23364S\"></sup>He gave orders to depart to the other side <i>of the sea</i>.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23365T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23365T\"></sup>Then a scribe came and said to Him, “Teacher, I will follow You wherever You go.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Jesus *said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“The foxes have holes and the birds of the air <i>have</i> nests, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23366U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23366U\"></sup>the Son of Man has nowhere to lay His head.”</span>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Another of the disciples said to Him, “Lord, permit me first to go and bury my father.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But Jesus *said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23368V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23368V\"></sup>Follow Me, and allow the dead to bury their own dead.”</span>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23369W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23369W\"></sup>When He got into the boat, His disciples followed Him.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And behold, there arose a great storm on the sea, so that the boat was being covered with the waves; but Jesus Himself was asleep.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And they came to <i>Him</i> and woke Him, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23371X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23371X\"></sup>Save <i>us</i>, Lord; we are perishing!”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>He *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Why are you afraid, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23372Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23372Y\"></sup>you men of little faith?”</span> Then He got up and rebuked the winds and the sea, and it became perfectly calm.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The men were amazed, and said, “What kind of a man is this, that even the winds and the sea obey Him?”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23374Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23374Z\"></sup>When He came to the other side into the country of the Gadarenes, two men who were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23374AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23374AA\"></sup>demon-possessed met Him as they were coming out of the tombs. <i>They were</i> so extremely violent that no one could pass by that way.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And they cried out, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23375AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23375AB\"></sup>What business do we have with each other, Son of God? Have You come here to torment us before the time?”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Now there was a herd of many swine feeding at a distance from them.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>The demons <i>began</i> to entreat Him, saying, “If You <i>are going to</i> cast us out, send us into the herd of swine.”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And He said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Go!”</span> And they came out and went into the swine, and the whole herd rushed down the steep bank into the sea and perished in the waters.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>The herdsmen ran away, and went to the city and reported everything, including what had happened to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23379AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23379AC\"></sup>demoniacs.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And behold, the whole city came out to meet Jesus; and when they saw Him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23380AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23380AD\"></sup>they implored Him to leave their region."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">9 </span>Getting into a boat, Jesus crossed over <i>the sea</i> and came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23381A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23381A\"></sup>His own city.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23382B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23382B\"></sup>And they brought to Him a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23382C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23382C\"></sup>paralytic lying on a bed. Seeing their faith, Jesus said to the paralytic, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23382D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23382D\"></sup>Take courage, son; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23382E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23382E\"></sup>your sins are forgiven.”</span>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And some of the scribes said to themselves, “This <i>fellow</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23383F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23383F\"></sup>blasphemes.”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23384G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23384G\"></sup>knowing their thoughts said, <span class=\"woj\">“Why are you thinking evil in your hearts?</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Which is easier, to say, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23385H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23385H\"></sup>Your sins are forgiven,’ or to say, ‘Get up, and walk’?</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But so that you may know that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23386I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23386I\"></sup>the Son of Man has authority on earth to forgive sins”</span>—then He *said to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23386J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23386J\"></sup>paralytic, <span class=\"woj\">“Get up, pick up your bed and go home.”</span>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And he got up and went home.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But when the crowds saw <i>this</i>, they were awestruck, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23388K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23388K\"></sup>glorified God, who had given such authority to men.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23389L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23389L\"></sup>As Jesus went on from there, He saw a man called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23389M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23389M\"></sup>Matthew, sitting in the tax collector’s booth; and He *said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23389N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23389N\"></sup>Follow Me!”</span> And he got up and followed Him.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then it happened that as Jesus was reclining <i>at the table</i> in the house, behold, many tax collectors and sinners came and were dining with Jesus and His disciples.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>When the Pharisees saw <i>this</i>, they said to His disciples, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23391O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23391O\"></sup>Why is your Teacher eating with the tax collectors and sinners?”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But when Jesus heard <i>this</i>, He said, <span class=\"woj\">“<i>It is</i> not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23392P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23392P\"></sup>those who are healthy who need a physician, but those who are sick.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But go and learn <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23393Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23393Q\"></sup>what this means: ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23393R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23393R\"></sup>I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">desire</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">compassion</span>, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">and not sacrifice</span>,’ for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23393S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23393S\"></sup>I did not come to call the righteous, but sinners.”</span>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Then the disciples of John *came to Him, asking, “Why do we and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23394T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23394T\"></sup>the Pharisees fast, but Your disciples do not fast?”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“The attendants of the bridegroom cannot mourn as long as the bridegroom is with them, can they? But the days will come when the bridegroom is taken away from them, and then they will fast.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But no one puts a patch of unshrunk cloth on an old garment; for the patch pulls away from the garment, and a worse tear results.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Nor do <i>people</i> put new wine into old wineskins; otherwise the wineskins burst, and the wine pours out and the wineskins are ruined; but they put new wine into fresh wineskins, and both are preserved.”</span>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23398U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23398U\"></sup>While He was saying these things to them, a <i>synagogue</i> official came and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23398V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23398V\"></sup>bowed down before Him, and said, “My daughter has just died; but come and lay Your hand on her, and she will live.”",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Jesus got up and <i>began</i> to follow him, and <i>so did</i> His disciples.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And a woman who had been suffering from a hemorrhage for twelve years, came up behind Him and touched <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23400W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23400W\"></sup>the fringe of His cloak;",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>for she was saying to herself, “If I only <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23401X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23401X\"></sup>touch His garment, I will get well.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But Jesus turning and seeing her said, <span class=\"woj\">“Daughter, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23402Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23402Y\"></sup>take courage; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23402Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23402Z\"></sup>your faith has made you well.”</span> At once the woman was made well.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>When Jesus came into the official’s house, and saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23403AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23403AA\"></sup>the flute-players and the crowd in noisy disorder,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>He said, <span class=\"woj\">“Leave; for the girl <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23404AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23404AB\"></sup>has not died, but is asleep.”</span> And they <i>began</i> laughing at Him.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23405AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23405AC\"></sup>when the crowd had been sent out, He entered and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23405AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23405AD\"></sup>took her by the hand, and the girl got up.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23406AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23406AE\"></sup>This news spread throughout all that land.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>As Jesus went on from there, two blind men followed Him, crying out, “Have mercy on us, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23407AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23407AF\"></sup>Son of David!”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>When He entered the house, the blind men came up to Him, and Jesus *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Do you believe that I am able to do this?”</span> They *said to Him, “Yes, Lord.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Then He touched their eyes, saying, <span class=\"woj\">“It shall be done to you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23409AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23409AG\"></sup>according to your faith.”</span>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And their eyes were opened. And Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23410AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23410AH\"></sup>sternly warned them: <span class=\"woj\">“See that no one knows <i>about this</i>!”</span>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>But they went out and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23411AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23411AI\"></sup>spread the news about Him throughout all that land.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>As they were going out, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23412AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23412AJ\"></sup>a mute, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23412AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23412AK\"></sup>demon-possessed man was brought to Him.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>After the demon was cast out, the mute man spoke; and the crowds were amazed, <i>and were</i> saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23413AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23413AL\"></sup>Nothing like this has ever been seen in Israel.”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>But the Pharisees were saying, “He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23414AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23414AM\"></sup>casts out the demons by the ruler of the demons.”",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Jesus was going through all the cities and villages, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23415AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23415AN\"></sup>teaching in their synagogues and proclaiming the gospel of the kingdom, and healing every kind of disease and every kind of sickness.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23416AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23416AO\"></sup>Seeing the people, He felt compassion for them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23416AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23416AP\"></sup>because they were distressed and dispirited like sheep without a shepherd.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Then He *said to His disciples, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23417AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23417AQ\"></sup>The harvest is plentiful, but the workers are few.</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Therefore beseech the Lord of the harvest to send out workers into His harvest.”</span>"
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">10 </span>Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23419A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23419A\"></sup>summoned His twelve disciples and gave them authority over unclean spirits, to cast them out, and to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23419B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23419B\"></sup>heal every kind of disease and every kind of sickness.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23420C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23420C\"></sup>Now the names of the twelve apostles are these: The first, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23420D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23420D\"></sup>Simon, who is called Peter, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23420E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23420E\"></sup>Andrew his brother; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23420F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23420F\"></sup>James the son of Zebedee, and John his brother;",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23421G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23421G\"></sup>Philip and Bartholomew; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23421H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23421H\"></sup>Thomas and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23421I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23421I\"></sup>Matthew the tax collector; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23421J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23421J\"></sup>James the son of Alphaeus, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23421K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23421K\"></sup>Thaddaeus;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Simon the Zealot, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23422L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23422L\"></sup>Judas Iscariot, the one who betrayed Him.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23423M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23423M\"></sup>These twelve Jesus sent out after instructing them: <span class=\"woj\">“Do not go in <i>the</i> way of <i>the</i> Gentiles, and do not enter <i>any</i> city of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23423N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23423N\"></sup>Samaritans;</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>but rather go to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23424O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23424O\"></sup>the lost sheep of the house of Israel.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And as you go, preach, saying, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23425P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23425P\"></sup>The kingdom of heaven is at hand.’</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Heal <i>the</i> sick, raise <i>the</i> dead, cleanse <i>the</i> lepers, cast out demons. Freely you received, freely give.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23427Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23427Q\"></sup>Do not acquire gold, or silver, or copper for your money belts,</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>or a bag for <i>your</i> journey, or even two coats, or sandals, or a staff; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23428R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23428R\"></sup>the worker is worthy of his support.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And whatever city or village you enter, inquire who is worthy in it, and stay at his house until you leave <i>that city</i>.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>As you enter the house, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23430S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23430S\"></sup>give it your greeting.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>If the house is worthy, give it your <i>blessing of</i> peace. But if it is not worthy, take back your <i>blessing of</i> peace.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Whoever does not receive you, nor heed your words, as you go out of that house or that city, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23432T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23432T\"></sup>shake the dust off your feet.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Truly I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23433U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23433U\"></sup>it will be more tolerable for <i>the</i> land of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23433V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23433V\"></sup>Sodom and Gomorrah in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23433W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23433W\"></sup>the day of judgment than for that city.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23434X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23434X\"></sup>Behold, I send you out as sheep in the midst of wolves; so be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23434Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23434Y\"></sup>shrewd as serpents and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23434Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23434Z\"></sup>innocent as doves.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>But beware of men, for they will hand you over to <i>the</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23435AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23435AA\"></sup>courts and scourge you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23435AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23435AB\"></sup>in their synagogues;</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>and you will even be brought before governors and kings for My sake, as a testimony to them and to the Gentiles.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23437AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23437AC\"></sup>But when they hand you over, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23437AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23437AD\"></sup>do not worry about how or what you are to say; for it will be given you in that hour what you are to say.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23438AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23438AE\"></sup>it is not you who speak, but <i>it is</i> the Spirit of your Father who speaks in you.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23439AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23439AF\"></sup>Brother will betray brother to death, and a father <i>his</i> child; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23439AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23439AG\"></sup>children will rise up against parents and cause them to be put to death.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23440AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23440AH\"></sup>You will be hated by all because of My name, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23440AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23440AI\"></sup>it is the one who has endured to the end who will be saved.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“But whenever they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23441AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23441AJ\"></sup>persecute you in one city, flee to the next; for truly I say to you, you will not finish <i>going through</i> the cities of Israel <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23441AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23441AK\"></sup>until the Son of Man comes.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23442AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23442AL\"></sup>A disciple is not above his teacher, nor a slave above his master.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>It is enough for the disciple that he become like his teacher, and the slave like his master. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23443AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23443AM\"></sup>If they have called the head of the house <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23443AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23443AN\"></sup>Beelzebul, how much more <i>will they malign</i> the members of his household!</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“Therefore do not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23444AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23444AO\"></sup>fear them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23444AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23444AP\"></sup>for there is nothing concealed that will not be revealed, or hidden that will not be known.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23445AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23445AQ\"></sup>What I tell you in the darkness, speak in the light; and what you hear <i>whispered</i> in <i>your</i> ear, proclaim <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23445AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23445AR\"></sup>upon the housetops.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Do not fear those who kill the body but are unable to kill the soul; but rather <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23446AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23446AS\"></sup>fear Him who is able to destroy both soul and body in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23446AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23446AT\"></sup>hell.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23447AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23447AU\"></sup>Are not two sparrows sold for a cent? And <i>yet</i> not one of them will fall to the ground apart from your Father.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23448AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23448AV\"></sup>the very hairs of your head are all numbered.</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>So do not fear; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23449AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23449AW\"></sup>you are more valuable than many sparrows.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23450AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23450AX\"></sup>everyone who confesses Me before men, I will also confess him before My Father who is in heaven.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23451AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23451AY\"></sup>whoever denies Me before men, I will also deny him before My Father who is in heaven.</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23452AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23452AZ\"></sup>Do not think that I came to bring peace on the earth; I did not come to bring peace, but a sword.</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>For I came to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23453BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23453BA\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">set a man against his father, and a daughter against her mother, and a daughter-in-law against her mother-in-law</span>;</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23454BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23454BB\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">a man’s enemies will be the members of his household</span>.</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23455BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23455BC\"></sup>He who loves father or mother more than Me is not worthy of Me; and he who loves son or daughter more than Me is not worthy of Me.</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23456BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23456BD\"></sup>he who does not take his cross and follow after Me is not worthy of Me.</span>",
			"39": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23457BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23457BE\"></sup>He who has found his life will lose it, and he who has lost his life for My sake will find it.</span>",
			"40": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23458BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23458BF\"></sup>He who receives you receives Me, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23458BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23458BG\"></sup>he who receives Me receives Him who sent Me.</span>",
			"41": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23459BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23459BH\"></sup>He who receives a prophet in <i>the</i> name of a prophet shall receive a prophet’s reward; and he who receives a righteous man in the name of a righteous man shall receive a righteous man’s reward.</span>",
			"42": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23460BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23460BI\"></sup>whoever in the name of a disciple gives to one of these little ones even a cup of cold water to drink, truly I say to you, he shall not lose his reward.”</span>"
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">11 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23461A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23461A\"></sup>When Jesus had finished giving instructions to His twelve disciples, He departed from there <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23461B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23461B\"></sup>to teach and preach in their cities.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23462C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23462C\"></sup>Now when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23462D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23462D\"></sup>John, while imprisoned, heard of the works of Christ, he sent <i>word</i> by his disciples",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and said to Him, “Are You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23463E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23463E\"></sup>the Expected One, or shall we look for someone else?”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Jesus answered and said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Go and report to John what you hear and see:</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23465F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23465F\"></sup><i>the</i> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">blind receive sight</span> and <i>the</i> lame walk, <i>the</i> lepers are cleansed and <i>the</i> deaf hear, <i>the</i> dead are raised up, and <i>the</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23465G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23465G\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">poor have the</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">gospel preached to them</span>.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And blessed is he who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23466H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23466H\"></sup>does not take offense at Me.”</span>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>As these men were going <i>away</i>, Jesus began to speak to the crowds about John, <span class=\"woj\">“What did you go out into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23467I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23467I\"></sup>the wilderness to see? A reed shaken by the wind?</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But what did you go out to see? A man dressed in soft <i>clothing</i>? Those who wear soft <i>clothing</i> are in kings’ palaces!</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But what did you go out to see? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23469J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23469J\"></sup>A prophet? Yes, I tell you, and one who is more than a prophet.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>This is the one about whom it is written,</span><span class=\"woj\">‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23470K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23470K\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Behold</span>, I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">send My messenger</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">ahead of You</span>,</span><span class=\"woj\"><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Who will prepare Your way before You</span>.’</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Truly I say to you, among those born of women there has not arisen <i>anyone</i> greater than John the Baptist! Yet the one who is least in the kingdom of heaven is greater than he.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23472L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23472L\"></sup>From the days of John the Baptist until now the kingdom of heaven suffers violence, and violent men take it by force.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For all the prophets and the Law prophesied until John.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And if you are willing to accept <i>it</i>, John himself is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23474M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23474M\"></sup>Elijah who was to come.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23475N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23475N\"></sup>He who has ears to hear, let him hear.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“But to what shall I compare this generation? It is like children sitting in the market places, who call out to the other <i>children</i>,</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>and say, ‘We played the flute for you, and you did not dance; we sang a dirge, and you did not mourn.’</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For John came neither <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23478O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23478O\"></sup>eating nor <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23478P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23478P\"></sup>drinking, and they say, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23478Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23478Q\"></sup>He has a demon!’</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The Son of Man came eating and drinking, and they say, ‘Behold, a gluttonous man and a drunkard, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23479R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23479R\"></sup>a friend of tax collectors and sinners!’ Yet wisdom is vindicated by her deeds.”</span>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Then He began to denounce the cities in which most of His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23480S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23480S\"></sup>miracles were done, because they did not repent.",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23481T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23481T\"></sup>Woe to you, Chorazin! Woe to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23481U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23481U\"></sup>Bethsaida! For if the miracles had occurred in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23481V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23481V\"></sup>Tyre and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23481W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23481W\"></sup>Sidon which occurred in you, they would have repented long ago in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23481X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23481X\"></sup>sackcloth and ashes.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Nevertheless I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23482Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23482Y\"></sup>it will be more tolerable for Tyre and Sidon in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23482Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23482Z\"></sup><i>the</i> day of judgment than for you.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23483AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23483AA\"></sup>Capernaum, will not be exalted to heaven, will you? You will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23483AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23483AB\"></sup>descend to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23483AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23483AC\"></sup>Hades; for if the miracles had occurred in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23483AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23483AD\"></sup>Sodom which occurred in you, it would have remained to this day.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Nevertheless I say to you that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23484AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23484AE\"></sup>it will be more tolerable for the land of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23484AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23484AF\"></sup>Sodom in <i>the</i> day of judgment, than for you.”</span>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23485AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23485AG\"></sup>At that time Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\">“I praise You, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23485AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23485AH\"></sup>Father, Lord of heaven and earth, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23485AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23485AI\"></sup>You have hidden these things from <i>the</i> wise and intelligent and have revealed them to infants.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Yes, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23486AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23486AJ\"></sup>Father, for this way was well-pleasing in Your sight.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23487AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23487AK\"></sup>All things have been handed over to Me by My Father; and no one knows the Son except the Father; nor does anyone know the Father <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23487AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23487AL\"></sup>except the Son, and anyone to whom the Son wills to reveal <i>Him</i>.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23488AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23488AM\"></sup>Come to Me, all who are weary and heavy-laden, and I will give you rest.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Take My yoke upon you and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23489AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23489AN\"></sup>learn from Me, for I am gentle and humble in heart, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23489AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23489AO\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">you will find rest for your souls</span>.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23490AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23490AP\"></sup>My yoke is easy and My burden is light.”</span>"
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">12 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23491A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23491A\"></sup>At that time Jesus went through the grainfields on the Sabbath, and His disciples became hungry and began to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23491B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23491B\"></sup>pick the heads <i>of grain</i> and eat.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>But when the Pharisees saw <i>this</i>, they said to Him, “Look, Your disciples do what <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23492C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23492C\"></sup>is not lawful to do on a Sabbath.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>But He said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Have you not read what David did when he became hungry, he and his companions,</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>how he entered the house of God, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23494D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23494D\"></sup>they ate the consecrated bread, which was not lawful for him to eat nor for those with him, but for the priests alone?</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Or have you not read in the Law, that on the Sabbath the priests in the temple break the Sabbath and are innocent?</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But I say to you that something <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23496E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23496E\"></sup>greater than the temple is here.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But if you had known what this means, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23497F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23497F\"></sup>I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">desire</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">compassion, and not a sacrifice</span>,’ you would not have condemned the innocent.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23498G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23498G\"></sup>the Son of Man is Lord of the Sabbath.”</span>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23499H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23499H\"></sup>Departing from there, He went into their synagogue.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And a man <i>was there</i> whose hand was withered. And they questioned Jesus, asking, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23500I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23500I\"></sup>Is it lawful to heal on the Sabbath?”—so that they might accuse Him.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And He said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23501J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23501J\"></sup>What man is there among you who has a sheep, and if it falls into a pit on the Sabbath, will he not take hold of it and lift it out?</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23502K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23502K\"></sup>How much more valuable then is a man than a sheep! So then, it is lawful to do good on the Sabbath.”</span>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then He *said to the man, <span class=\"woj\">“Stretch out your hand!”</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23503L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23503L\"></sup>He stretched it out, and it was restored to normal, like the other.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But the Pharisees went out and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23504M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23504M\"></sup>conspired against Him, <i>as to</i> how they might destroy Him.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But Jesus, aware of <i>this</i>, withdrew from there. Many followed Him, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23505N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23505N\"></sup>He healed them all,",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23506O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23506O\"></sup>warned them not to tell who He was.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><i>This was</i> to fulfill what was spoken through Isaiah the prophet:",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23508P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23508P\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Behold, My</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Servant whom</span> I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">have chosen</span>;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23508Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23508Q\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">My Beloved in whom My soul</span> is <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">well-pleased</span>;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23508R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23508R\"></sup>I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">will put My Spirit upon Him</span>,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23508S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23508S\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And He shall proclaim</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">justice to the</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Gentiles</span>.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23509T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23509T\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">He will not quarrel, nor cry out</span>;<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Nor will anyone hear His voice in the streets</span>.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23510U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23510U\"></sup>A <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">battered reed He will not break off</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And a smoldering wick He will not put out</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Until He</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">leads</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">justice to victory</span>.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23511V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23511V\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And in His name the</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Gentiles will hope</span>.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23512W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23512W\"></sup>Then a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23512X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23512X\"></sup>demon-possessed man <i>who was</i> blind and mute was brought to Jesus, and He healed him, so that the mute man spoke and saw.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>All the crowds were amazed, and were saying, “This man cannot be the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23513Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23513Y\"></sup>Son of David, can he?”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>But when the Pharisees heard <i>this</i>, they said, “This man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23514Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23514Z\"></sup>casts out demons only by Beelzebul the ruler of the demons.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23515AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23515AA\"></sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23515AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23515AB\"></sup>knowing their thoughts Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Any kingdom divided against itself is laid waste; and any city or house divided against itself will not stand.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>If <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23516AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23516AC\"></sup>Satan casts out Satan, he is divided against himself; how then will his kingdom stand?</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>If I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23517AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23517AD\"></sup>by Beelzebul cast out demons, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23517AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23517AE\"></sup>by whom do your sons cast <i>them</i> out? For this reason they will be your judges.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23518AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23518AF\"></sup>if I cast out demons by the Spirit of God, then the kingdom of God has come upon you.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>Or how can anyone enter the strong man’s house and carry off his property, unless he first binds the strong <i>man</i>? And then he will plunder his house.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23520AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23520AG\"></sup>He who is not with Me is against Me; and he who does not gather with Me scatters.</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23521AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23521AH\"></sup>Therefore I say to you, any sin and blasphemy shall be forgiven people, but blasphemy against the Spirit shall not be forgiven.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23522AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23522AI\"></sup>Whoever speaks a word against the Son of Man, it shall be forgiven him; but whoever speaks against the Holy Spirit, it shall not be forgiven him, either in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23522AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23522AJ\"></sup>this age or in the <i>age</i> to come.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“Either make the tree good and its fruit good, or make the tree bad and its fruit bad; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23523AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23523AK\"></sup>the tree is known by its fruit.</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23524AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23524AL\"></sup>You brood of vipers, how can you, being evil, speak what is good? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23524AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23524AM\"></sup>For the mouth speaks out of that which fills the heart.</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23525AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23525AN\"></sup>The good man brings out of <i>his</i> good treasure what is good; and the evil man brings out of <i>his</i> evil treasure what is evil.</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>But I tell you that every careless word that people speak, they shall give an accounting for it in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23526AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23526AO\"></sup>the day of judgment.</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>For by your words you will be justified, and by your words you will be condemned.”</span>",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Then some of the scribes and Pharisees said to Him, “Teacher, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23528AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23528AP\"></sup>we want to see a sign from You.”",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>But He answered and said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23529AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23529AQ\"></sup>An evil and adulterous generation craves for a sign; and <i>yet</i> no sign will be given to it but the sign of Jonah the prophet;</span>",
			"40": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>for just as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23530AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23530AR\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Jonah was three days and three nights in the belly of the sea monster</span>, so will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23530AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23530AS\"></sup>the Son of Man be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23530AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23530AT\"></sup>three days and three nights in the heart of the earth.</span>",
			"41": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23531AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23531AU\"></sup>The men of Nineveh will stand up with this generation at the judgment, and will condemn it because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23531AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23531AV\"></sup>they repented at the preaching of Jonah; and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23531AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23531AW\"></sup>something greater than Jonah is here.</span>",
			"42": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23532AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23532AX\"></sup><i>The</i> Queen of <i>the</i> South will rise up with this generation at the judgment and will condemn it, because she came from the ends of the earth to hear the wisdom of Solomon; and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23532AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23532AY\"></sup>something greater than Solomon is here.</span>",
			"43": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23533AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23533AZ\"></sup>Now when the unclean spirit goes out of a man, it passes through waterless places seeking rest, and does not find <i>it</i>.</span>",
			"44": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>Then it says, ‘I will return to my house from which I came’; and when it comes, it finds <i>it</i> unoccupied, swept, and put in order.</span>",
			"45": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>Then it goes and takes along with it seven other spirits more wicked than itself, and they go in and live there; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23535BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23535BA\"></sup>the last state of that man becomes worse than the first. That is the way it will also be with this evil generation.”</span>",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23536BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23536BB\"></sup>While He was still speaking to the crowds, behold, His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23536BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23536BC\"></sup>mother and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23536BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23536BD\"></sup>brothers were standing outside, seeking to speak to Him.",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>Someone said to Him, “Behold, Your mother and Your brothers are standing outside seeking to speak to You.”",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>But Jesus answered the one who was telling Him and said, <span class=\"woj\">“Who is My mother and who are My brothers?”</span>",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>And stretching out His hand toward His disciples, He said, <span class=\"woj\">“Behold My mother and My brothers!</span>",
			"50": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>For whoever does the will of My Father who is in heaven, he is My brother and sister and mother.”</span>"
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">13 </span>That day Jesus went out of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23541A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23541A\"></sup>the house and was sitting <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23541B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23541B\"></sup>by the sea.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And large crowds gathered to Him, so <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23542C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23542C\"></sup>He got into a boat and sat down, and the whole crowd was standing on the beach.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And He spoke many things to them in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23543D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23543D\"></sup>parables, saying, <span class=\"woj\">“Behold, the sower went out to sow;</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and as he sowed, some <i>seeds</i> fell beside the road, and the birds came and ate them up.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Others fell on the rocky places, where they did not have much soil; and immediately they sprang up, because they had no depth of soil.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But when the sun had risen, they were scorched; and because they had no root, they withered away.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Others fell among the thorns, and the thorns came up and choked them out.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And others fell on the good soil and *yielded a crop, some a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23548E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23548E\"></sup>hundredfold, some sixty, and some thirty.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23549F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23549F\"></sup>He who has ears, let him hear.”</span>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And the disciples came and said to Him, “Why do You speak to them in parables?”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Jesus answered them, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23551G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23551G\"></sup>To you it has been granted to know the mysteries of the kingdom of heaven, but to them it has not been granted.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23552H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23552H\"></sup>For whoever has, to him <i>more</i> shall be given, and he will have an abundance; but whoever does not have, even what he has shall be taken away from him.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Therefore I speak to them in parables; because while <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23553I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23553I\"></sup>seeing they do not see, and while hearing they do not hear, nor do they understand.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>In their case the prophecy of Isaiah is being fulfilled, which says,</span><span class=\"woj\">‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23554J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23554J\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You will keep on hearing</span>, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">but will not understand</span>;</span><span class=\"woj\"><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You will keep on seeing, but will not perceive</span>;</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23555K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23555K\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">For the heart of this people has become dull</span>,</span><span class=\"woj\"><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">With their ears they scarcely hear</span>,</span><span class=\"woj\"><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And they have closed their eyes</span>,</span><span class=\"woj\"><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Otherwise they would see with their eyes</span>,</span><span class=\"woj\"><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Hear with their ears</span>,</span><span class=\"woj\"><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And understand with their heart and return</span>,</span><span class=\"woj\"><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And I would heal them</span>.’</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23556L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23556L\"></sup>But blessed are your eyes, because they see; and your ears, because they hear.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>For truly I say to you that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23557M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23557M\"></sup>many prophets and righteous men desired to see what you see, and did not see <i>it</i>, and to hear what you hear, and did not hear <i>it</i>.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23558N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23558N\"></sup>Hear then the parable of the sower.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>When anyone hears <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23559O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23559O\"></sup>the word of the kingdom and does not understand it, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23559P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23559P\"></sup>the evil <i>one</i> comes and snatches away what has been sown in his heart. This is the one on whom seed was sown beside the road.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The one on whom seed was sown on the rocky places, this is the man who hears the word and immediately receives it with joy;</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>yet he has no <i>firm</i> root in himself, but is <i>only</i> temporary, and when affliction or persecution arises because of the word, immediately he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23561Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23561Q\"></sup>falls away.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And the one on whom seed was sown among the thorns, this is the man who hears the word, and the worry of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23562R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23562R\"></sup>the world and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23562S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23562S\"></sup>deceitfulness of wealth choke the word, and it becomes unfruitful.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And the one on whom seed was sown on the good soil, this is the man who hears the word and understands it; who indeed bears fruit and brings forth, some <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23563T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23563T\"></sup>a hundredfold, some sixty, and some thirty.”</span>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Jesus presented another parable to them, saying, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23564U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23564U\"></sup>The kingdom of heaven may be compared to a man who sowed good seed in his field.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But while his men were sleeping, his enemy came and sowed tares among the wheat, and went away.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>But when the wheat sprouted and bore grain, then the tares became evident also.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>The slaves of the landowner came and said to him, ‘Sir, did you not sow good seed in your field? How then does it have tares?’</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And he said to them, ‘An enemy has done this!’ The slaves *said to him, ‘Do you want us, then, to go and gather them up?’</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>But he *said, ‘No; for while you are gathering up the tares, you may uproot the wheat with them.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Allow both to grow together until the harvest; and in the time of the harvest I will say to the reapers, “First gather up the tares and bind them in bundles to burn them up; but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23570V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23570V\"></sup>gather the wheat into my barn.”’”</span>",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>He presented another parable to them, saying, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23571W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23571W\"></sup>The kingdom of heaven is like <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23571X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23571X\"></sup>a mustard seed, which a man took and sowed in his field;</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>and this is smaller than all <i>other</i> seeds, but when it is full grown, it is larger than the garden plants and becomes a tree, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23572Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23572Y\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">the birds of the</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">air</span> come and <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">nest in its branches</span>.”</span>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>He spoke another parable to them, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23573Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23573Z\"></sup>The kingdom of heaven is like leaven, which a woman took and hid in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23573AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23573AA\"></sup>three pecks of flour until it was all leavened.”</span>",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>All these things Jesus spoke to the crowds in parables, and He did not speak to them <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23574AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23574AB\"></sup>without a parable.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><i>This was</i> to fulfill what was spoken through the prophet:“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23575AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23575AC\"></sup>I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">will open My mouth in parables</span>;I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">will utter things hidden since the foundation of the world</span>.”",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Then He left the crowds and went into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23576AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23576AD\"></sup>the house. And His disciples came to Him and said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23576AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23576AE\"></sup>Explain to us the parable of the tares of the field.”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>And He said, <span class=\"woj\">“The one who sows the good seed is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23577AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23577AF\"></sup>the Son of Man,</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>and the field is the world; and <i>as for</i> the good seed, these are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23578AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23578AG\"></sup>the sons of the kingdom; and the tares are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23578AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23578AH\"></sup>the sons of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23578AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23578AI\"></sup>the evil <i>one</i>;</span>",
			"39": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>and the enemy who sowed them is the devil, and the harvest is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23579AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23579AJ\"></sup>the end of the age; and the reapers are angels.</span>",
			"40": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>So just as the tares are gathered up and burned with fire, so shall it be at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23580AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23580AK\"></sup>the end of the age.</span>",
			"41": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23581AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23581AL\"></sup>The Son of Man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23581AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23581AM\"></sup>will send forth His angels, and they will gather out of His kingdom all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23581AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23581AN\"></sup>stumbling blocks, and those who commit lawlessness,</span>",
			"42": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23582AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23582AO\"></sup>will throw them into the furnace of fire; in that place <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23582AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23582AP\"></sup>there will be weeping and gnashing of teeth.</span>",
			"43": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23583AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23583AQ\"></sup>Then <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">the righteous will shine forth as the sun</span> in the kingdom of their Father. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23583AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23583AR\"></sup>He who has ears, let him hear.</span>",
			"44": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23584AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23584AS\"></sup>The kingdom of heaven is like a treasure hidden in the field, which a man found and hid <i>again</i>; and from joy over it he goes and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23584AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23584AT\"></sup>sells all that he has and buys that field.</span>",
			"45": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>“Again, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23585AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23585AU\"></sup>the kingdom of heaven is like a merchant seeking fine pearls,</span>",
			"46": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>and upon finding one pearl of great value, he went and sold all that he had and bought it.</span>",
			"47": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>“Again, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23587AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23587AV\"></sup>the kingdom of heaven is like a dragnet cast into the sea, and gathering <i>fish</i> of every kind;</span>",
			"48": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>and when it was filled, they drew it up on the beach; and they sat down and gathered the good <i>fish</i> into containers, but the bad they threw away.</span>",
			"49": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>So it will be at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23589AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23589AW\"></sup>the end of the age; the angels will come forth and take out the wicked from among the righteous,</span>",
			"50": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23590AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23590AX\"></sup>will throw them into the furnace of fire; in that place <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23590AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23590AY\"></sup>there will be weeping and gnashing of teeth.</span>",
			"51": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>“Have you understood all these things?”</span> They *said to Him, “Yes.”",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>And Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Therefore every scribe who has become a disciple of the kingdom of heaven is like a head of a household, who brings out of his treasure things new and old.”</span>",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23593AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23593AZ\"></sup>When Jesus had finished these parables, He departed from there.",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23594BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23594BA\"></sup>He came to His hometown and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23594BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23594BB\"></sup><i>began</i> teaching them in their synagogue, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23594BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23594BC\"></sup>they were astonished, and said, “Where <i>did</i> this man <i>get</i> this wisdom and <i>these</i> miraculous powers?",
			"55": "<sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup>Is not this the carpenter’s son? Is not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23595BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23595BD\"></sup>His mother called Mary, and His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23595BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23595BE\"></sup>brothers, James and Joseph and Simon and Judas?",
			"56": "<sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23596BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23596BF\"></sup>His sisters, are they not all with us? Where then <i>did</i> this man <i>get</i> all these things?”",
			"57": "<sup class=\"versenum\">57 </sup>And they took <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23597BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23597BG\"></sup>offense at Him. But Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23597BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23597BH\"></sup>A prophet is not without honor except in his hometown and in his <i>own</i> household.”</span>",
			"58": "<sup class=\"versenum\">58 </sup>And He did not do many miracles there because of their unbelief."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">14 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23599A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23599A\"></sup>At that time <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23599B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23599B\"></sup>Herod the tetrarch heard the news about Jesus,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and said to his servants, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23600C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23600C\"></sup>This is John the Baptist; he has risen from the dead, and that is why miraculous powers are at work in him.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23601D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23601D\"></sup>Herod had John arrested, he bound him and put him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23601E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23601E\"></sup>in prison because of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23601F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23601F\"></sup>Herodias, the wife of his brother Philip.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For John had been saying to him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23602G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23602G\"></sup>It is not lawful for you to have her.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Although Herod wanted to put him to death, he feared the crowd, because they regarded John as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23603H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23603H\"></sup>a prophet.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But when Herod’s birthday came, the daughter of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23604I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23604I\"></sup>Herodias danced before <i>them</i> and pleased <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23604J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23604J\"></sup>Herod,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>so <i>much</i> that he promised with an oath to give her whatever she asked.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Having been prompted by her mother, she *said, “Give me here on a platter the head of John the Baptist.”",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Although he was grieved, the king commanded <i>it</i> to be given because of his oaths, and because of his dinner guests.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>He sent and had John beheaded in the prison.",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And his head was brought on a platter and given to the girl, and she brought it to her mother.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>His disciples came and took away the body and buried it; and they went and reported to Jesus.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23611K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23611K\"></sup>Now when Jesus heard <i>about John</i>, He withdrew from there in a boat to a secluded place by Himself; and when the people heard <i>of this</i>, they followed Him on foot from the cities.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>When He went ashore, He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23612L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23612L\"></sup>saw a large crowd, and felt compassion for them and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23612M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23612M\"></sup>healed their sick.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>When it was evening, the disciples came to Him and said, “This place is desolate and the hour is already late; so send the crowds away, that they may go into the villages and buy food for themselves.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“They do not need to go away; you give them <i>something</i> to eat!”</span>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>They *said to Him, “We have here only <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23615N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23615N\"></sup>five loaves and two fish.”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And He said, <span class=\"woj\">“Bring them here to Me.”</span>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Ordering the people to sit down on the grass, He took the five loaves and the two fish, and looking up toward heaven, He <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23617O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23617O\"></sup>blessed <i>the food</i>, and breaking the loaves He gave them to the disciples, and the disciples <i>gave them</i> to the crowds,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>and they all ate and were satisfied. They picked up what was left over of the broken pieces, twelve full <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23618P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23618P\"></sup>baskets.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>There were about five thousand men who ate, besides women and children.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23620Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23620Q\"></sup>Immediately He made the disciples get into the boat and go ahead of Him to the other side, while He sent the crowds away.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>After He had sent the crowds away, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23621R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23621R\"></sup>He went up on the mountain by Himself to pray; and when it was evening, He was there alone.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>But the boat was already a long distance from the land, battered by the waves; for the wind was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23622S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23622S\"></sup>contrary.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23623T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23623T\"></sup>the fourth watch of the night He came to them, walking on the sea.",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>When the disciples saw Him walking on the sea, they were terrified, and said, “It is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23624U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23624U\"></sup>a ghost!” And they cried out in fear.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But immediately Jesus spoke to them, saying, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23625V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23625V\"></sup>Take courage, it is I; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23625W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23625W\"></sup>do not be afraid.”</span>",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Peter said to Him, “Lord, if it is You, command me to come to You on the water.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And He said, <span class=\"woj\">“Come!”</span> And Peter got out of the boat, and walked on the water and came toward Jesus.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>But seeing the wind, he became frightened, and beginning to sink, he cried out, “Lord, save me!”",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Immediately Jesus stretched out His hand and took hold of him, and *said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23629X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23629X\"></sup>You of little faith, why did you doubt?”</span>",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>When they got into the boat, the wind stopped.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>And those who were in the boat worshiped Him, saying, “You are certainly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23631Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23631Y\"></sup>God’s Son!”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23632Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23632Z\"></sup>When they had crossed over, they came to land at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23632AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23632AA\"></sup>Gennesaret.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>And when the men of that place recognized Him, they sent <i>word</i> into all that surrounding district and brought to Him all who were sick;",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>and they implored Him that they might just touch <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23634AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23634AB\"></sup>the fringe of His cloak; and as many as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23634AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23634AC\"></sup>touched <i>it</i> were cured."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">15 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23635A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23635A\"></sup>Then some Pharisees and scribes *came to Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23635B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23635B\"></sup>from Jerusalem and said,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“Why do Your disciples break the tradition of the elders? For they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23636C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23636C\"></sup>do not wash their hands when they eat bread.”",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And He answered and said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Why do you yourselves transgress the commandment of God for the sake of your tradition?</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>For God said, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23638D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23638D\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Honor your father and mother</span>,’ and, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23638E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23638E\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">He who speaks evil of father or mother is to</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">be put to death</span>.’</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But you say, ‘Whoever says to <i>his</i> father or mother, “Whatever I have that would help you has been given <i>to God</i>,”</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>he is not to honor his father or his mother.’ And <i>by this</i> you invalidated the word of God for the sake of your tradition.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>You hypocrites, rightly did Isaiah prophesy of you:</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23642F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23642F\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">This people honors Me with their lips</span>,</span><span class=\"woj\"><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">But their heart is far away from Me</span>.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>‘<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">But in vain do they worship Me</span>,</span><span class=\"woj\"><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Teaching as</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23643G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23643G\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">doctrines the precepts of men</span>.’”</span>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>After Jesus called the crowd to Him, He said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Hear and understand.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23645H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23645H\"></sup><i>It is</i> not what enters into the mouth <i>that</i> defiles the man, but what proceeds out of the mouth, this defiles the man.”</span>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then the disciples *came and *said to Him, “Do You know that the Pharisees were offended when they heard this statement?”",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But He answered and said, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23647I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23647I\"></sup>Every plant which My heavenly Father did not plant shall be uprooted.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Let them alone; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23648J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23648J\"></sup>they are blind guides of the blind. And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23648K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23648K\"></sup>if a blind man guides a blind man, both will fall into a pit.”</span>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Peter said to Him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23649L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23649L\"></sup>Explain the parable to us.”",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\">“Are you still lacking in understanding also?</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Do you not understand that everything that goes into the mouth passes into the stomach, and is eliminated?</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23652M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23652M\"></sup>the things that proceed out of the mouth come from the heart, and those defile the man.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23653N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23653N\"></sup>For out of the heart come evil thoughts, murders, adulteries, fornications, thefts, false witness, slanders.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>These are the things which defile the man; but to eat with unwashed hands does not defile the man.”</span>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23655O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23655O\"></sup>Jesus went away from there, and withdrew into the district of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23655P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23655P\"></sup>Tyre and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23655Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23655Q\"></sup>Sidon.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And a Canaanite woman from that region came out and <i>began</i> to cry out, saying, “Have mercy on me, Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23656R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23656R\"></sup>Son of David; my daughter is cruelly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23656S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23656S\"></sup>demon-possessed.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But He did not answer her a word. And His disciples came and implored Him, saying, “Send her away, because she keeps shouting at us.”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>But He answered and said, <span class=\"woj\">“I was sent only to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23658T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23658T\"></sup>the lost sheep of the house of Israel.”</span>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But she came and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23659U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23659U\"></sup><i>began</i> to bow down before Him, saying, “Lord, help me!”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And He answered and said, <span class=\"woj\">“It is not good to take the children’s bread and throw it to the dogs.”</span>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>But she said, “Yes, Lord; but even the dogs feed on the crumbs which fall from their masters’ table.”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Then Jesus said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“O woman, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23662V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23662V\"></sup>your faith is great; it shall be done for you as you wish.”</span> And her daughter was healed at once.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23663W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23663W\"></sup>Departing from there, Jesus went along by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23663X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23663X\"></sup>the Sea of Galilee, and having gone up on the mountain, He was sitting there.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And large crowds came to Him, bringing with them <i>those who were</i> lame, crippled, blind, mute, and many others, and they laid them down at His feet; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23664Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23664Y\"></sup>He healed them.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>So the crowd marveled as they saw the mute speaking, the crippled restored, and the lame walking, and the blind seeing; and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23665Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23665Z\"></sup>glorified the God of Israel.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23666AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23666AA\"></sup>And Jesus called His disciples to Him, and said, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23666AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23666AB\"></sup>I feel compassion for the people, because they have remained with Me now three days and have nothing to eat; and I do not want to send them away hungry, for they might faint on the way.”</span>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>The disciples *said to Him, “Where would we get so many loaves in <i>this</i> desolate place to satisfy such a large crowd?”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And Jesus *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“How many loaves do you have?”</span> And they said, “Seven, and a few small fish.”",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>And He directed the people to sit down on the ground;",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>and He took the seven loaves and the fish; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23670AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23670AC\"></sup>giving thanks, He broke them and started giving them to the disciples, and the disciples <i>gave them</i> to the people.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>And they all ate and were satisfied, and they picked up what was left over of the broken pieces, seven large <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23671AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23671AD\"></sup>baskets full.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>And those who ate were four thousand men, besides women and children.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>And sending away the crowds, Jesus got into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23673AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23673AE\"></sup>the boat and came to the region of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23673AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23673AF\"></sup>Magadan."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">16 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23674A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23674A\"></sup>The <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23674B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23674B\"></sup>Pharisees and Sadducees came up, and testing Jesus, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23674C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23674C\"></sup>asked Him to show them a sign from heaven.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>But He replied to them, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23675D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23675D\"></sup>When it is evening, you say, ‘<i>It will be</i> fair weather, for the sky is red.’</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And in the morning, ‘<i>There will be</i> a storm today, for the sky is red and threatening.’ <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23676E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23676E\"></sup>Do you know how to discern the appearance of the sky, but cannot <i>discern</i> the signs of the times?</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23677F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23677F\"></sup>An evil and adulterous generation seeks after a sign; and a sign will not be given it, except the sign of Jonah.”</span> And He left them and went away.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And the disciples came to the other side <i>of the sea</i>, but they had forgotten to bring <i>any</i> bread.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Watch out and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23679G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23679G\"></sup>beware of the leaven of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23679H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23679H\"></sup>Pharisees and Sadducees.”</span>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>They began to discuss <i>this</i> among themselves, saying, “<i>He said that</i> because we did not bring <i>any</i> bread.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But Jesus, aware of this, said, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23681I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23681I\"></sup>You men of little faith, why do you discuss among yourselves that you have no bread?</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Do you not yet understand or remember <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23682J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23682J\"></sup>the five loaves of the five thousand, and how many baskets <i>full</i> you picked up?</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23683K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23683K\"></sup>the seven loaves of the four thousand, and how many large baskets <i>full</i> you picked up?</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>How is it that you do not understand that I did not speak to you concerning bread? But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23684L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23684L\"></sup>beware of the leaven of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23684M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23684M\"></sup>Pharisees and Sadducees.”</span>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Then they understood that He did not say to beware of the leaven of bread, but of the teaching of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23685N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23685N\"></sup>Pharisees and Sadducees.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23686O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23686O\"></sup>Now when Jesus came into the district of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23686P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23686P\"></sup>Caesarea Philippi, He was asking His disciples, <span class=\"woj\">“Who do people say that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23686Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23686Q\"></sup>the Son of Man is?”</span>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And they said, “Some <i>say</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23687R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23687R\"></sup>John the Baptist; and others, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23687S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23687S\"></sup>Elijah; but still others, Jeremiah, or one of the prophets.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>He *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“But who do you say that I am?”</span>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Simon Peter answered, “You are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23689T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23689T\"></sup>the Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23689U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23689U\"></sup>the Son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23689V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23689V\"></sup>the living God.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Blessed are you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23690W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23690W\"></sup>Simon Barjona, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23690X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23690X\"></sup>flesh and blood did not reveal <i>this</i> to you, but My Father who is in heaven.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I also say to you that you are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23691Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23691Y\"></sup>Peter, and upon this rock I will build My church; and the gates of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23691Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23691Z\"></sup>Hades will not overpower it.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>I will give you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23692AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23692AA\"></sup>the keys of the kingdom of heaven; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23692AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23692AB\"></sup>whatever you bind on earth shall have been bound in heaven, and whatever you loose on earth shall have been loosed in heaven.”</span>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23693AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23693AC\"></sup>Then He warned the disciples that they should tell no one that He was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23693AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23693AD\"></sup>the Christ.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23694AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23694AE\"></sup>From that time Jesus began to show His disciples that He must go to Jerusalem, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23694AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23694AF\"></sup>suffer many things from the elders and chief priests and scribes, and be killed, and be raised up on the third day.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Peter took Him aside and began to rebuke Him, saying, “God forbid <i>it</i>, Lord! This shall never happen to You.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>But He turned and said to Peter, <span class=\"woj\">“Get behind Me, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23696AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23696AG\"></sup>Satan! You are a stumbling block to Me; for you are not setting your mind on God’s interests, but man’s.”</span>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Then Jesus said to His disciples, <span class=\"woj\">“If anyone wishes to come after Me, he must deny himself, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23697AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23697AH\"></sup>take up his cross and follow Me.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23698AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23698AI\"></sup>whoever wishes to save his life will lose it; but whoever loses his life for My sake will find it.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>For what will it profit a man if he gains the whole world and forfeits his soul? Or what will a man give in exchange for his soul?</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23700AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23700AJ\"></sup>Son of Man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23700AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23700AK\"></sup>is going to come in the glory of His Father with His angels, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23700AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23700AL\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">will then</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">repay every man according to his</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">deeds</span>.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“Truly I say to you, there are some of those who are standing here who will not taste death until they see the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23701AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23701AM\"></sup>Son of Man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23701AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23701AN\"></sup>coming in His kingdom.”</span>"
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">17 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23702A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23702A\"></sup>Six days later Jesus *took with Him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23702B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23702B\"></sup>Peter and James and John his brother, and *led them up on a high mountain by themselves.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And He was transfigured before them; and His face shone like the sun, and His garments became as white as light.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And behold, Moses and Elijah appeared to them, talking with Him.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Peter said to Jesus, “Lord, it is good for us to be here; if You wish, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23705C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23705C\"></sup>I will make three tabernacles here, one for You, and one for Moses, and one for Elijah.”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>While he was still speaking, a bright cloud overshadowed them, and behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23706D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23706D\"></sup>a voice out of the cloud said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23706E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23706E\"></sup>This is My beloved Son, with whom I am well-pleased; listen to Him!”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>When the disciples heard <i>this</i>, they fell face down to the ground and were terrified.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And Jesus came to <i>them</i> and touched them and said, <span class=\"woj\">“Get up, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23708F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23708F\"></sup>do not be afraid.”</span>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And lifting up their eyes, they saw no one except Jesus Himself alone.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23710G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23710G\"></sup>As they were coming down from the mountain, Jesus commanded them, saying, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23710H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23710H\"></sup>Tell the vision to no one until <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23710I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23710I\"></sup>the Son of Man has <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23710J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23710J\"></sup>risen from the dead.”</span>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And His disciples asked Him, “Why then do the scribes say that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23711K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23711K\"></sup>Elijah must come first?”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And He answered and said, <span class=\"woj\">“Elijah is coming and will restore all things;</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>but I say to you that Elijah already came, and they did not recognize him, but did to him whatever they wished. So also <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23713L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23713L\"></sup>the Son of Man is going to suffer at their hands.”</span>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then the disciples understood that He had spoken to them about John the Baptist.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23715M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23715M\"></sup>When they came to the crowd, a man came up to Jesus, falling on his knees before Him and saying,",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Lord, have mercy on my son, for he is a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23716N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23716N\"></sup>lunatic and is very ill; for he often falls into the fire and often into the water.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>I brought him to Your disciples, and they could not cure him.”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And Jesus answered and said, <span class=\"woj\">“You unbelieving and perverted generation, how long shall I be with you? How long shall I put up with you? Bring him here to Me.”</span>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And Jesus rebuked him, and the demon came out of him, and the boy was cured at once.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Then the disciples came to Jesus privately and said, “Why could we not drive it out?”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And He *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Because of the littleness of your faith; for truly I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23721O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23721O\"></sup>if you have faith the size of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23721P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23721P\"></sup>a mustard seed, you will say to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23721Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23721Q\"></sup>this mountain, ‘Move from here to there,’ and it will move; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23721R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23721R\"></sup>nothing will be impossible to you.</span>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>[<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23722S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23722S\"></sup>But this kind does not go out except by prayer and fasting.”</span>]",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23723T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23723T\"></sup>And while they were gathering together in Galilee, Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“The Son of Man is going to be delivered into the hands of men;</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23724U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23724U\"></sup>they will kill Him, and He will be raised on the third day.”</span> And they were deeply grieved.",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>When they came to Capernaum, those who collected <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23725V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23725V\"></sup>the two-drachma <i>tax</i> came to Peter and said, “Does your teacher not pay <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23725W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23725W\"></sup>the two-drachma <i>tax</i>?”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>He *said, “Yes.” And when he came into the house, Jesus spoke to him first, saying, <span class=\"woj\">“What do you think, Simon? From whom do the kings of the earth collect <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23726X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23726X\"></sup>customs or <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23726Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23726Y\"></sup>poll-tax, from their sons or from strangers?”</span>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>When Peter said, “From strangers,” Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Then the sons are exempt.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>However, so that we do not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23728Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23728Z\"></sup>offend them, go to the sea and throw in a hook, and take the first fish that comes up; and when you open its mouth, you will find a shekel. Take that and give it to them for you and Me.”</span>"
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">18 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23729A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23729A\"></sup>At that time the disciples came to Jesus and said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23729B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23729B\"></sup>Who then is greatest in the kingdom of heaven?”",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And He called a child to Himself and set him before them,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>and said, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly I say to you, unless you are converted and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23731C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23731C\"></sup>become like children, you will not enter the kingdom of heaven.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Whoever then humbles himself as this child, he is the greatest in the kingdom of heaven.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And whoever receives one such child in My name receives Me;</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23734D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23734D\"></sup>whoever <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23734E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23734E\"></sup>causes one of these little ones who believe in Me to stumble, it would be better for him to have a heavy millstone hung around his neck, and to be drowned in the depth of the sea.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>“Woe to the world because of <i>its</i> stumbling blocks! For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23735F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23735F\"></sup>it is inevitable that stumbling blocks come; but woe to that man through whom the stumbling block comes!</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23736G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23736G\"></sup>If your hand or your foot causes you to stumble, cut it off and throw it from you; it is better for you to enter life crippled or lame, than to have two hands or two feet and be cast into the eternal fire.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23737H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23737H\"></sup>If your eye causes you to stumble, pluck it out and throw it from you. It is better for you to enter life with one eye, than to have two eyes and be cast into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23737I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23737I\"></sup>fiery hell.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>“See that you do not despise one of these little ones, for I say to you that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23738J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23738J\"></sup>their angels in heaven continually see the face of My Father who is in heaven.</span>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>[<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23739K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23739K\"></sup>For the Son of Man has come to save that which was lost.</span>]",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>“What do you think? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23740L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23740L\"></sup>If any man has a hundred sheep, and one of them has gone astray, does he not leave the ninety-nine on the mountains and go and search for the one that is straying?</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>If it turns out that he finds it, truly I say to you, he rejoices over it more than over the ninety-nine which have not gone astray.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>So it is not <i>the</i> will of your Father who is in heaven that one of these little ones perish.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23743M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23743M\"></sup>If your brother sins, go and show him his fault in private; if he listens to you, you have won your brother.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But if he does not listen <i>to you</i>, take one or two more with you, so that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23744N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23744N\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">by the mouth of two or three witnesses every</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">fact may be confirmed</span>.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>If he refuses to listen to them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23745O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23745O\"></sup>tell it to the church; and if he refuses to listen even to the church, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23745P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23745P\"></sup>let him be to you as a Gentile and a tax collector.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Truly I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23746Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23746Q\"></sup>whatever you bind on earth shall have been bound in heaven; and whatever you loose on earth shall have been loosed in heaven.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Again I say to you, that if two of you agree on earth about anything that they may ask, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23747R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23747R\"></sup>it shall be done for them by My Father who is in heaven.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>For where two or three have gathered together in My name, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23748S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23748S\"></sup>I am there in their midst.”</span>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Then Peter came and said to Him, “Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23749T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23749T\"></sup>how often shall my brother sin against me and I forgive him? Up to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23749U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23749U\"></sup>seven times?”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Jesus *said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“I do not say to you, up to seven times, but up to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23750V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23750V\"></sup>seventy times seven.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“For this reason <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23751W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23751W\"></sup>the kingdom of heaven may be compared to a king who wished to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23751X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23751X\"></sup>settle accounts with his slaves.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>When he had begun to settle <i>them</i>, one who owed him ten thousand talents was brought to him.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>But since he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23753Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23753Y\"></sup>did not have <i>the means</i> to repay, his lord commanded him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23753Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23753Z\"></sup>to be sold, along with his wife and children and all that he had, and repayment to be made.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>So the slave fell <i>to the ground</i> and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23754AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23754AA\"></sup>prostrated himself before him, saying, ‘Have patience with me and I will repay you everything.’</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And the lord of that slave felt compassion and released him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23755AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23755AB\"></sup>forgave him the debt.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>But that slave went out and found one of his fellow slaves who owed him a hundred denarii; and he seized him and <i>began</i> to choke <i>him</i>, saying, ‘Pay back what you owe.’</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>So his fellow slave fell <i>to the ground</i> and <i>began</i> to plead with him, saying, ‘Have patience with me and I will repay you.’</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>But he was unwilling and went and threw him in prison until he should pay back what was owed.</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>So when his fellow slaves saw what had happened, they were deeply grieved and came and reported to their lord all that had happened.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Then summoning him, his lord *said to him, ‘You wicked slave, I forgave you all that debt because you pleaded with me.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23761AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23761AC\"></sup>Should you not also have had mercy on your fellow slave, in the same way that I had mercy on you?’</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>And his lord, moved with anger, handed him over to the torturers until he should repay all that was owed him.</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23763AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23763AD\"></sup>My heavenly Father will also do the same to you, if each of you does not forgive his brother from your heart.”</span>"
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">19 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23764A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23764A\"></sup>When Jesus had finished these words, He departed from Galilee and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23764B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23764B\"></sup>came into the region of Judea beyond the Jordan;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and large crowds followed Him, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23765C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23765C\"></sup>He healed them there.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><i>Some</i> Pharisees came to Jesus, testing Him and asking, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23766D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23766D\"></sup>Is it lawful <i>for a man</i> to divorce his wife for any reason at all?”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And He answered and said, <span class=\"woj\">“Have you not read <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23767E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23767E\"></sup>that He who created <i>them</i> from the beginning <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">made them male and female</span>,</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>and said, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23768F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23768F\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">For this reason a man shall leave his father and mother and be joined to his wife, and</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23768G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23768G\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">the two shall become one flesh</span>’?</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So they are no longer two, but one flesh. What therefore God has joined together, let no man separate.”</span>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>They *said to Him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23770H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23770H\"></sup>Why then did Moses command to <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">give her a certificate of divorce and send</span> <i>her</i> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">away</span>?”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>He *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Because of your hardness of heart Moses permitted you to divorce your wives; but from the beginning it has not been this way.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23772I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23772I\"></sup>whoever divorces his wife, except for immorality, and marries another woman commits adultery.”</span>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>The disciples *said to Him, “If the relationship of the man with his wife is like this, it is better not to marry.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>But He said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23774J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23774J\"></sup>Not all men <i>can</i> accept this statement, but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23774K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23774K\"></sup><i>only</i> those to whom it has been given.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For there are eunuchs who were born that way from their mother’s womb; and there are eunuchs who were made eunuchs by men; and there are <i>also</i> eunuchs who made themselves eunuchs for the sake of the kingdom of heaven. He who is able to accept <i>this</i>, let him accept <i>it</i>.”</span>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23776L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23776L\"></sup>Then <i>some</i> children were brought to Him so that He might lay His hands on them and pray; and the disciples rebuked them.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>But Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23777M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23777M\"></sup>Let the children alone, and do not hinder them from coming to Me; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23777N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23777N\"></sup>the kingdom of heaven belongs to such as these.”</span>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>After laying His hands on them, He departed from there.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23779O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23779O\"></sup>And someone came to Him and said, “Teacher, what good thing shall I do that I may obtain <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23779P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23779P\"></sup>eternal life?”",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And He said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Why are you asking Me about what is good? There is <i>only</i> One who is good; but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23780Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23780Q\"></sup>if you wish to enter into life, keep the commandments.”</span>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><i>Then</i> he *said to Him, “Which ones?” And Jesus said, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23781R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23781R\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You shall not commit murder; You shall not commit adultery; You shall not steal; You shall not bear false witness</span>;</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23782S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23782S\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Honor your father and mother</span>; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23782T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23782T\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You shall love your neighbor as yourself</span>.”</span>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The young man *said to Him, “All these things I have kept; what am I still lacking?”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“If you wish to be complete, go <i>and</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23784U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23784U\"></sup>sell your possessions and give to <i>the</i> poor, and you will have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23784V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23784V\"></sup>treasure in heaven; and come, follow Me.”</span>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But when the young man heard this statement, he went away grieving; for he was one who owned much property.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And Jesus said to His disciples, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23786W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23786W\"></sup>it is hard for a rich man to enter the kingdom of heaven.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Again I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23787X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23787X\"></sup>it is easier for a camel to go through the eye of a needle, than for a rich man to enter the kingdom of God.”</span>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>When the disciples heard <i>this</i>, they were very astonished and said, “Then who can be saved?”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>And looking at <i>them</i> Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23789Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23789Y\"></sup>With people this is impossible, but with God all things are possible.”</span>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Then Peter said to Him, “Behold, we have left everything and followed You; what then will there be for us?”",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>And Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly I say to you, that you who have followed Me, in the regeneration when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23791Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23791Z\"></sup>the Son of Man will sit on His glorious throne, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23791AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23791AA\"></sup>you also shall sit upon twelve thrones, judging the twelve tribes of Israel.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23792AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23792AB\"></sup>everyone who has left houses or brothers or sisters or father or mother or children or farms for My name’s sake, will receive many times as much, and will inherit eternal life.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23793AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23793AC\"></sup>But many <i>who are</i> first will be last; and <i>the</i> last, first.</span>"
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<span class=\"woj\"><span class=\"chapternum\">20 </span>“For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23794A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23794A\"></sup>the kingdom of heaven is like a landowner who went out early in the morning to hire laborers for his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23794B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23794B\"></sup>vineyard.</span>",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>When he had agreed with the laborers for a denarius for the day, he sent them into his vineyard.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And he went out about the third hour and saw others standing idle in the market place;</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and to those he said, ‘You also go into the vineyard, and whatever is right I will give you.’ And <i>so</i> they went.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Again he went out about the sixth and the ninth hour, and did the same thing.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>And about the eleventh <i>hour</i> he went out and found others standing <i>around</i>; and he *said to them, ‘Why have you been standing here idle all day long?’</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>They *said to him, ‘Because no one hired us.’ He *said to them, ‘You go into the vineyard too.’</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>“When <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23801C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23801C\"></sup>evening came, the owner of the vineyard *said to his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23801D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23801D\"></sup>foreman, ‘Call the laborers and pay them their wages, beginning with the last <i>group</i> to the first.’</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>When those <i>hired</i> about the eleventh hour came, each one received a denarius.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>When those <i>hired</i> first came, they thought that they would receive more; but each of them also received a denarius.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>When they received it, they grumbled at the landowner,</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>saying, ‘These last men have worked <i>only</i> one hour, and you have made them equal to us who have borne the burden and the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23805E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23805E\"></sup>scorching heat of the day.’</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>But he answered and said to one of them, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23806F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23806F\"></sup>Friend, I am doing you no wrong; did you not agree with me for a denarius?</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Take what is yours and go, but I wish to give to this last man the same as to you.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Is it not lawful for me to do what I wish with what is my own? Or is your <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23808G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23808G\"></sup>eye envious because I am generous?’</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>So <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23809H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23809H\"></sup>the last shall be first, and the first last.”</span>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23810I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23810I\"></sup>As Jesus was about to go up to Jerusalem, He took the twelve <i>disciples</i> aside by themselves, and on the way He said to them,",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>“Behold, we are going up to Jerusalem; and the Son of Man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23811J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23811J\"></sup>will be delivered to the chief priests and scribes, and they will condemn Him to death,</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23812K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23812K\"></sup>will hand Him over to the Gentiles to mock and scourge and crucify <i>Him</i>, and on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23812L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23812L\"></sup>the third day He will be raised up.”</span>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23813M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23813M\"></sup>Then the mother of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23813N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23813N\"></sup>the sons of Zebedee came to Jesus with her sons, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23813O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23813O\"></sup>bowing down and making a request of Him.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And He said to her, <span class=\"woj\">“What do you wish?”</span> She *said to Him, “Command that in Your kingdom these two sons of mine <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23814P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23814P\"></sup>may sit one on Your right and one on Your left.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But Jesus answered, <span class=\"woj\">“You do not know what you are asking. Are you able <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23815Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23815Q\"></sup>to drink the cup that I am about to drink?”</span> They *said to Him, “We are able.”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>He *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23816R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23816R\"></sup>My cup you shall drink; but to sit on My right and on <i>My</i> left, this is not Mine to give, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23816S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23816S\"></sup>but it is for those for whom it has been <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23816T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23816T\"></sup>prepared by My Father.”</span>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>And hearing <i>this</i>, the ten became indignant with the two brothers.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23818U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23818U\"></sup>But Jesus called them to Himself and said, <span class=\"woj\">“You know that the rulers of the Gentiles lord it over them, and <i>their</i> great men exercise authority over them.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>It is not this way among you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23819V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23819V\"></sup>but whoever wishes to become great among you shall be your servant,</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>and whoever wishes to be first among you shall be your slave;</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>just as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23821W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23821W\"></sup>the Son of Man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23821X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23821X\"></sup>did not come to be served, but to serve, and to give His life a ransom for many.”</span>",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23822Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23822Y\"></sup>As they were leaving Jericho, a large crowd followed Him.",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And two blind men sitting by the road, hearing that Jesus was passing by, cried out, “Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23823Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23823Z\"></sup>have mercy on us, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23823AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23823AA\"></sup>Son of David!”",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>The crowd sternly told them to be quiet, but they cried out all the more, “Lord, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23824AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23824AB\"></sup>Son of David, have mercy on us!”",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>And Jesus stopped and called them, and said, <span class=\"woj\">“What do you want Me to do for you?”</span>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>They *said to Him, “Lord, <i>we want</i> our eyes to be opened.”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Moved with compassion, Jesus touched their eyes; and immediately they regained their sight and followed Him."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">21 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23828A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23828A\"></sup>When they had approached Jerusalem and had come to Bethphage, at <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23828B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23828B\"></sup>the Mount of Olives, then Jesus sent two disciples,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>saying to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Go into the village opposite you, and immediately you will find a donkey tied <i>there</i> and a colt with her; untie them and bring them to Me.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>If anyone says anything to you, you shall say, ‘The Lord has need of them,’ and immediately he will send them.”</span>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23831C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23831C\"></sup>This took place to fulfill what was spoken through the prophet:",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23832D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23832D\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Say to the daughter of Zion</span>,‘<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Behold your King is coming to you</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Gentle, and mounted on a donkey</span>,<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Even on a colt, the foal of a beast of burden</span>.’”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The disciples went and did just as Jesus had instructed them,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>and brought the donkey and the colt, and laid their coats on them; and He sat on the coats.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Most of the crowd <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23835E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23835E\"></sup>spread their coats in the road, and others were cutting branches from the trees and spreading them in the road.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>The crowds going ahead of Him, and those who followed, were shouting,“Hosanna to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23836F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23836F\"></sup>Son of David;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23836G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23836G\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Blessed is He who comes in the name of the Lord</span>;Hosanna <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23836H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23836H\"></sup>in the highest!”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>When He had entered Jerusalem, all the city was stirred, saying, “Who is this?”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>And the crowds were saying, “This is <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23838I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23838I\"></sup>the prophet Jesus, from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23838J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23838J\"></sup>Nazareth in Galilee.”",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23839K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23839K\"></sup>And Jesus entered the temple and drove out all those who were buying and selling in the temple, and overturned the tables of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23839L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23839L\"></sup>money changers and the seats of those who were selling <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23839M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23839M\"></sup>doves.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>And He *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“It is written, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23840N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23840N\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">My house shall be called a house of prayer</span>’; but you are making it a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23840O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23840O\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">robbers</span>’ <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">den</span>.”</span>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And <i>the</i> blind and <i>the</i> lame came to Him in the temple, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23841P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23841P\"></sup>He healed them.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>But when the chief priests and the scribes saw the wonderful things that He had done, and the children who were shouting in the temple, “Hosanna to the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23842Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23842Q\"></sup>Son of David,” they became indignant",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>and said to Him, “Do You hear what these <i>children</i> are saying?” And Jesus *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Yes; have you never read, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23843R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23843R\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Out of the mouth of infants and nursing babies You have prepared praise for Yourself</span>’?”</span>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And He left them and went out of the city to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23844S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23844S\"></sup>Bethany, and spent the night there.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23845T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23845T\"></sup>Now in the morning, when He was returning to the city, He became hungry.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Seeing a lone <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23846U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23846U\"></sup>fig tree by the road, He came to it and found nothing on it except leaves only; and He *said to it, <span class=\"woj\">“No longer shall there ever be <i>any</i> fruit from you.”</span> And at once the fig tree withered.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Seeing <i>this</i>, the disciples were amazed and asked, “How did the fig tree wither <i>all</i> at once?”",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And Jesus answered and said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23848V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23848V\"></sup>if you have faith and do not doubt, you will not only do what was done to the fig tree, but even if you say to this mountain, ‘Be taken up and cast into the sea,’ it will happen.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23849W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23849W\"></sup>all things you ask in prayer, believing, you will receive.”</span>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23850X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23850X\"></sup>When He entered the temple, the chief priests and the elders of the people came to Him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23850Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23850Y\"></sup>while He was teaching, and said, “By what authority are You doing these things, and who gave You this authority?”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Jesus said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“I will also ask you one thing, which if you tell Me, I will also tell you by what authority I do these things.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>The baptism of John was from what <i>source</i>, from heaven or from men?”</span> And they <i>began</i> reasoning among themselves, saying, “If we say, ‘From heaven,’ He will say to us, ‘Then why did you not believe him?’",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>But if we say, ‘From men,’ we fear the people; for they all regard John as <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23853Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23853Z\"></sup>a prophet.”",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And answering Jesus, they said, “We do not know.” He also said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Neither will I tell you by what authority I do these things.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>“But what do you think? A man had two sons, and he came to the first and said, ‘Son, go work today in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23855AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23855AA\"></sup>vineyard.’</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>And he answered, ‘I will not’; but afterward he regretted it and went.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>The man came to the second and said the same thing; and he answered, ‘I <i>will</i>, sir’; but he did not go.</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Which of the two did the will of his father?”</span> They *said, “The first.” Jesus *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Truly I say to you that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23858AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23858AB\"></sup>the tax collectors and prostitutes will get into the kingdom of God before you.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>For John came to you in the way of righteousness and you did not believe him; but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23859AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23859AC\"></sup>the tax collectors and prostitutes did believe him; and you, seeing <i>this</i>, did not even feel remorse afterward so as to believe him.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>“Listen to another parable. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23860AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23860AD\"></sup>There was a landowner who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23860AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23860AE\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">planted a</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23860AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23860AF\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">vineyard and put a wall around it and dug a wine press in it, and built a tower</span>, and rented it out to vine-growers and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23860AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23860AG\"></sup>went on a journey.</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>When the harvest time approached, he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23861AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23861AH\"></sup>sent his slaves to the vine-growers to receive his produce.</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>The vine-growers took his slaves and beat one, and killed another, and stoned a third.</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Again he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23863AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23863AI\"></sup>sent another group of slaves larger than the first; and they did the same thing to them.</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>But afterward he sent his son to them, saying, ‘They will respect my son.’</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>But when the vine-growers saw the son, they said among themselves, ‘This is the heir; come, let us kill him and seize his inheritance.’</span>",
			"39": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>They took him, and threw him out of the vineyard and killed him.</span>",
			"40": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>Therefore when the owner of the vineyard comes, what will he do to those vine-growers?”</span>",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>They *said to Him, “He will bring those wretches to a wretched end, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23868AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23868AJ\"></sup>will rent out the vineyard to other vine-growers who will pay him the proceeds at the <i>proper</i> seasons.”",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>Jesus *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Did you never read in the Scriptures,</span><span class=\"woj\">‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23869AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23869AK\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">The stone which the builders rejected</span>,</span><span class=\"woj\"><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">This became the chief corner</span> <i>stone</i>;</span><span class=\"woj\"><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">This came about from the Lord</span>,</span><span class=\"woj\"><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And it is marvelous in our eyes</span>’?</span>",
			"43": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>Therefore I say to you, the kingdom of God will be taken away from you and given to a people, producing the fruit of it.</span>",
			"44": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23871AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23871AL\"></sup>he who falls on this stone will be broken to pieces; but on whomever it falls, it will scatter him like dust.”</span>",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>When the chief priests and the Pharisees heard His parables, they understood that He was speaking about them.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>When they sought to seize Him, they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23873AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23873AM\"></sup>feared the people, because they considered Him to be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23873AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23873AN\"></sup>prophet."
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">22 </span>Jesus spoke to them again in parables, saying,",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23875A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23875A\"></sup>The kingdom of heaven may be compared to a king who gave a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23875B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23875B\"></sup>wedding feast for his son.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23876C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23876C\"></sup>sent out his slaves to call those who had been invited to the wedding feast, and they were unwilling to come.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Again he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23877D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23877D\"></sup>sent out other slaves saying, ‘Tell those who have been invited, “Behold, I have prepared my dinner; my oxen and my fattened livestock are <i>all</i> butchered and everything is ready; come to the wedding feast.”’</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But they paid no attention and went their way, one to his own farm, another to his business,</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>and the rest seized his slaves and mistreated them and killed them.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>But the king was enraged, and he sent his armies and destroyed those murderers and set their city on fire.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>Then he *said to his slaves, ‘The wedding is ready, but those who were invited were not worthy.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Go therefore to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23882E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23882E\"></sup>the main highways, and as many as you find <i>there</i>, invite to the wedding feast.’</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Those slaves went out into the streets and gathered together all they found, both evil and good; and the wedding hall was filled with dinner guests.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>“But when the king came in to look over the dinner guests, he saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23884F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23884F\"></sup>a man there who was not dressed in wedding clothes,</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>and he *said to him, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23885G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23885G\"></sup>Friend, how did you come in here without wedding clothes?’ And the man was speechless.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then the king said to the servants, ‘Bind him hand and foot, and throw him into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23886H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23886H\"></sup>the outer darkness; in that place there will be weeping and gnashing of teeth.’</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>For many are <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23887I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23887I\"></sup>called, but few <i>are</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23887J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23887J\"></sup>chosen.”</span>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23888K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23888K\"></sup>Then the Pharisees went and plotted together how they might trap Him in what He said.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>And they *sent their disciples to Him, along with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23889L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23889L\"></sup>Herodians, saying, “Teacher, we know that You are truthful and teach the way of God in truth, and defer to no one; for You are not partial to any.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Tell us then, what do You think? Is it lawful to give a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23890M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23890M\"></sup>poll-tax to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23890N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23890N\"></sup>Caesar, or not?”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But Jesus perceived their malice, and said, <span class=\"woj\">“Why are you testing Me, you hypocrites?</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Show Me the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23892O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23892O\"></sup>coin <i>used</i> for the poll-tax.”</span> And they brought Him a denarius.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>And He *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Whose likeness and inscription is this?”</span>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>They *said to Him, “Caesar’s.” Then He *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23894P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23894P\"></sup>Then render to Caesar the things that are Caesar’s; and to God the things that are God’s.”</span>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And hearing <i>this</i>, they were amazed, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23895Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23895Q\"></sup>leaving Him, they went away.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23896R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23896R\"></sup>On that day <i>some</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23896S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23896S\"></sup>Sadducees (who say <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23896T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23896T\"></sup>there is no resurrection) came to Jesus and questioned Him,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>asking, “Teacher, Moses said, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23897U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23897U\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">If a man dies having no children, his brother as next of kin shall marry his wife, and raise up children for his brother</span>.’",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Now there were seven brothers with us; and the first married and died, and having no children left his wife to his brother;",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>so also the second, and the third, down to the seventh.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Last of all, the woman died.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>In the resurrection, therefore, whose wife of the seven will she be? For they all had <i>married</i> her.”",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>But Jesus answered and said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“You are mistaken, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23902V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23902V\"></sup>not understanding the Scriptures nor the power of God.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>For in the resurrection they neither <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23903W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23903W\"></sup>marry nor are given in marriage, but are like angels in heaven.</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>But regarding the resurrection of the dead, have you not read what was spoken to you by God:</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23905X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23905X\"></sup>I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">am the God of Abraham, and the God of Isaac, and the God of Jacob</span>’? He is not the God of the dead but of the living.”</span>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>When the crowds heard <i>this</i>, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23906Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23906Y\"></sup>they were astonished at His teaching.",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23907Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23907Z\"></sup>But when the Pharisees heard that Jesus had silenced <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23907AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23907AA\"></sup>the Sadducees, they gathered themselves together.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>One of them, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23908AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23908AB\"></sup>a lawyer, asked Him <i>a question</i>, testing Him,",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>“Teacher, which is the great commandment in the Law?”",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>And He said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23910AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23910AC\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You shall love the Lord your God with all your heart, and with all your soul, and with all your mind</span>.’</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>This is the great and foremost commandment.</span>",
			"39": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>The second is like it, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23912AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23912AD\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">You shall love your neighbor as yourself</span>.’</span>",
			"40": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23913AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23913AE\"></sup>On these two commandments depend the whole Law and the Prophets.”</span>",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23914AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23914AF\"></sup>Now while the Pharisees were gathered together, Jesus asked them a question:",
			"42": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>“What do you think about the Christ, whose son is He?”</span> They *said to Him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23915AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23915AG\"></sup><i>The son</i> of David.”",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>He *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Then how does David <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23916AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23916AH\"></sup>in the Spirit call Him ‘Lord,’ saying,</span>",
			"44": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23917AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23917AI\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">The Lord said to my Lord</span>,</span><span class=\"woj\">“<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Sit at My right hand</span>,</span><span class=\"woj\"><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Until I put Your enemies beneath Your feet</span>”’?</span>",
			"45": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>If David then calls Him ‘Lord,’ how is He his son?”</span>",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23919AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23919AJ\"></sup>No one was able to answer Him a word, nor did anyone dare from that day on to ask Him another question."
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">23 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23920A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23920A\"></sup>Then Jesus spoke to the crowds and to His disciples,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>saying: <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23921B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23921B\"></sup>The scribes and the Pharisees have seated themselves in the chair of Moses;</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>therefore all that they tell you, do and observe, but do not do according to their deeds; for they say <i>things</i> and do not do <i>them</i>.</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23923C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23923C\"></sup>They tie up heavy burdens and lay them on men’s shoulders, but they themselves are unwilling to move them with <i>so much as</i> a finger.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But they do all their deeds <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23924D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23924D\"></sup>to be noticed by men; for they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23924E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23924E\"></sup>broaden their phylacteries and lengthen <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23924F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23924F\"></sup>the tassels <i>of their garments</i>.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>They <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23925G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23925G\"></sup>love the place of honor at banquets and the chief seats in the synagogues,</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>and respectful greetings in the market places, and being called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23926H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23926H\"></sup>Rabbi by men.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23927I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23927I\"></sup>do not be called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23927J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23927J\"></sup>Rabbi; for One is your Teacher, and you are all brothers.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Do not call <i>anyone</i> on earth your father; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23928K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23928K\"></sup>One is your Father, He who is in heaven.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Do not be called leaders; for One is your Leader, <i>that is</i>, Christ.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23930L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23930L\"></sup>But the greatest among you shall be your servant.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23931M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23931M\"></sup>Whoever exalts himself shall be humbled; and whoever humbles himself shall be exalted.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23932N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23932N\"></sup>But woe to you, scribes and Pharisees, hypocrites, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23932O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23932O\"></sup>because you shut off the kingdom of heaven from people; for you do not enter in yourselves, nor do you allow those who are entering to go in.</span>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>[<span class=\"woj\">Woe to you, scribes and Pharisees, hypocrites, because <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23933P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23933P\"></sup>you devour widows’ houses, and for a pretense you make long prayers; therefore you will receive greater condemnation.</span>]",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Woe to you, scribes and Pharisees, hypocrites, because you travel around on sea and land to make one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23934Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23934Q\"></sup>proselyte; and when he becomes one, you make him twice as much a son of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23934R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23934R\"></sup>hell as yourselves.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>“Woe to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23935S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23935S\"></sup>blind guides, who say, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23935T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23935T\"></sup>Whoever swears by the temple, <i>that</i> is nothing; but whoever swears by the gold of the temple is obligated.’</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>You fools and blind men! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23936U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23936U\"></sup>Which is more important, the gold or the temple that sanctified the gold?</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And, ‘Whoever swears by the altar, <i>that</i> is nothing, but whoever swears by the offering on it, he is obligated.’</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>You blind men, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23938V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23938V\"></sup>which is more important, the offering, or the altar that sanctifies the offering?</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Therefore, whoever swears by the altar, swears <i>both</i> by the altar and by everything on it.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>And whoever swears by the temple, swears <i>both</i> by the temple and by Him who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23940W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23940W\"></sup>dwells within it.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>And whoever swears by heaven, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23941X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23941X\"></sup>swears <i>both</i> by the throne of God and by Him who sits upon it.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23942Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23942Y\"></sup>Woe to you, scribes and Pharisees, hypocrites! For you tithe mint and dill and cummin, and have neglected the weightier provisions of the law: justice and mercy and faithfulness; but these are the things you should have done without neglecting the others.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>You <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23943Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23943Z\"></sup>blind guides, who strain out a gnat and swallow a camel!</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>“Woe to you, scribes and Pharisees, hypocrites! For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23944AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23944AA\"></sup>you clean the outside of the cup and of the dish, but inside they are full of robbery and self-indulgence.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>You blind Pharisee, first <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23945AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23945AB\"></sup>clean the inside of the cup and of the dish, so that the outside of it may become clean also.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23946AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23946AC\"></sup>Woe to you, scribes and Pharisees, hypocrites! For you are like whitewashed tombs which on the outside appear beautiful, but inside they are full of dead men’s bones and all uncleanness.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>So you, too, outwardly appear righteous to men, but inwardly you are full of hypocrisy and lawlessness.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23948AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23948AD\"></sup>Woe to you, scribes and Pharisees, hypocrites! For you build the tombs of the prophets and adorn the monuments of the righteous,</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>and say, ‘If we had been <i>living</i> in the days of our fathers, we would not have been partners with them in <i>shedding</i> the blood of the prophets.’</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>So you testify against yourselves, that you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23950AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23950AE\"></sup>are sons of those who murdered the prophets.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>Fill up, then, the measure <i>of the guilt</i> of your fathers.</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>You serpents, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23952AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23952AF\"></sup>you brood of vipers, how will you escape the sentence of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23952AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23952AG\"></sup>hell?</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23953AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23953AH\"></sup>Therefore, behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23953AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23953AI\"></sup>I am sending you prophets and wise men and scribes; some of them you will kill and crucify, and some of them you will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23953AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23953AJ\"></sup>scourge in your synagogues, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23953AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23953AK\"></sup>persecute from city to city,</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>so that upon you may fall <i>the guilt of</i> all the righteous blood shed on earth, from the blood of righteous <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23954AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23954AL\"></sup>Abel to the blood of Zechariah, the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23954AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23954AM\"></sup>son of Berechiah, whom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23954AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23954AN\"></sup>you murdered between the temple and the altar.</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>Truly I say to you, all these things will come upon <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23955AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23955AO\"></sup>this generation.</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23956AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23956AP\"></sup>Jerusalem, Jerusalem, who <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23956AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23956AQ\"></sup>kills the prophets and stones those who are sent to her! How often I wanted to gather your children together, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23956AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23956AR\"></sup>the way a hen gathers her chicks under her wings, and you were unwilling.</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23957AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23957AS\"></sup>your house is being left to you desolate!</span>",
			"39": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>For I say to you, from now on you will not see Me until you say, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23958AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23958AT\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Blessed is He who comes in the name of the Lord</span>!’”</span>"
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">24 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23959A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23959A\"></sup>Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23959B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23959B\"></sup>came out from the temple and was going away when His disciples came up to point out the temple buildings to Him.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And He said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Do you not see all these things? Truly I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23960C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23960C\"></sup>not one stone here will be left upon another, which will not be torn down.”</span>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>As He was sitting on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23961D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23961D\"></sup>the Mount of Olives, the disciples came to Him privately, saying, “Tell us, when will these things happen, and what <i>will be</i> the sign of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23961E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23961E\"></sup>Your coming, and of the end of the age?”",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>And Jesus answered and said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23962F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23962F\"></sup>See to it that no one misleads you.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23963G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23963G\"></sup>many will come in My name, saying, ‘I am the Christ,’ and will mislead many.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>You will be hearing of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23964H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23964H\"></sup>wars and rumors of wars. See that you are not frightened, for <i>those things</i> must take place, but <i>that</i> is not yet the end.</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23965I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23965I\"></sup>nation will rise against nation, and kingdom against kingdom, and in various places there will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23965J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23965J\"></sup>famines and earthquakes.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23966K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23966K\"></sup>But all these things are <i>merely</i> the beginning of birth pangs.</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23967L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23967L\"></sup>Then they will deliver you to tribulation, and will kill you, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23967M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23967M\"></sup>you will be hated by all nations because of My name.</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>At that time many will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23968N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23968N\"></sup>fall away and will betray one another and hate one another.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Many <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23969O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23969O\"></sup>false prophets will arise and will mislead many.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Because lawlessness is increased, most people’s love will grow cold.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23971P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23971P\"></sup>But the one who endures to the end, he will be saved.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>This <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23972Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23972Q\"></sup>gospel of the kingdom <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23972R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23972R\"></sup>shall be preached in the whole <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23972S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23972S\"></sup>world as a testimony to all the nations, and then the end will come.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>“Therefore when you see the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23973T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23973T\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">abomination of desolation</span> which was spoken of through Daniel the prophet, standing in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23973U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23973U\"></sup>the holy place</span> (<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23973V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23973V\"></sup>let the reader understand),",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>then those who are in Judea must flee to the mountains.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Whoever is on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23975W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23975W\"></sup>the housetop must not go down to get the things out that are in his house.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Whoever is in the field must not turn back to get his cloak.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23977X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23977X\"></sup>woe to those who are pregnant and to those who are nursing babies in those days!</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But pray that your flight will not be in the winter, or on a Sabbath.</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>For then there will be a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23979Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23979Y\"></sup>great tribulation, such as has not occurred since the beginning of the world until now, nor ever will.</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Unless those days had been cut short, no life would have been saved; but for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23980Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23980Z\"></sup>the sake of the elect those days will be cut short.</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23981AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23981AA\"></sup>Then if anyone says to you, ‘Behold, here is the Christ,’ or ‘There <i>He is</i>,’ do not believe <i>him</i>.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>For false Christs and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23982AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23982AB\"></sup>false prophets will arise and will show great <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23982AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23982AC\"></sup>signs and wonders, so as to mislead, if possible, even <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23982AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23982AD\"></sup>the elect.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Behold, I have told you in advance.</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>So if they say to you, ‘Behold, He is in the wilderness,’ do not go out, <i>or</i>, ‘Behold, He is in the inner rooms,’ do not believe <i>them</i>.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23985AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23985AE\"></sup>For just as the lightning comes from the east and flashes even to the west, so will the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23985AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23985AF\"></sup>coming of the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23985AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23985AG\"></sup>Son of Man be.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23986AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23986AH\"></sup>Wherever the corpse is, there the vultures will gather.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“But immediately after the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23987AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23987AI\"></sup>tribulation of those days <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23987AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23987AJ\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">the sun will be darkened, and the moon will not give its light, and</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23987AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23987AK\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">the stars will fall</span> from the sky, and the powers of the heavens will be shaken.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>And then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23988AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23988AL\"></sup>the sign of the Son of Man will appear in the sky, and then all the tribes of the earth will mourn, and they will see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23988AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23988AM\"></sup>the <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Son of Man coming on the clouds of the sky</span> with power and great glory.</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23989AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23989AN\"></sup>He will send forth His angels with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23989AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23989AO\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">a great trumpet</span> and <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">they will gather together</span> His <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23989AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23989AP\"></sup>elect from <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23989AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23989AQ\"></sup>the four winds, from one end of the sky to the other.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>“Now learn the parable from the fig tree: when its branch has already become tender and puts forth its leaves, you know that summer is near;</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>so, you too, when you see all these things, recognize that He is near, <i>right</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23991AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23991AR\"></sup>at the door.</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Truly I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23992AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23992AS\"></sup>this generation will not pass away until all these things take place.</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23993AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23993AT\"></sup>Heaven and earth will pass away, but My words will not pass away.</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>“But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23994AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23994AU\"></sup>of that day and hour no one knows, not even the angels of heaven, nor the Son, but the Father alone.</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>For the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23995AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23995AV\"></sup>coming of the Son of Man will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23995AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23995AW\"></sup>just like the days of Noah.</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>For as in those days before the flood they were eating and drinking, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23996AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23996AX\"></sup>marrying and giving in marriage, until the day that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23996AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23996AY\"></sup>Noah entered the ark,</span>",
			"39": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>and they did not understand until the flood came and took them all away; so will the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23997AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23997AZ\"></sup>coming of the Son of Man be.</span>",
			"40": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>Then there will be two men in the field; one will be taken and one will be left.</span>",
			"41": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23999BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23999BA\"></sup>Two women <i>will be</i> grinding at the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-23999BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-23999BB\"></sup>mill; one will be taken and one will be left.</span>",
			"42": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>“Therefore <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24000BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24000BC\"></sup>be on the alert, for you do not know which day your Lord is coming.</span>",
			"43": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>But be sure of this, that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24001BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24001BD\"></sup>if the head of the house had known <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24001BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24001BE\"></sup>at what time of the night the thief was coming, he would have been on the alert and would not have allowed his house to be broken into.</span>",
			"44": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>For this reason <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24002BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24002BF\"></sup>you also must be ready; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24002BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24002BG\"></sup>the Son of Man is coming at an hour when you do not think <i>He will</i>.</span>",
			"45": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24003BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24003BH\"></sup>Who then is the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24003BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24003BI\"></sup>faithful and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24003BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24003BJ\"></sup>sensible slave whom his master <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24003BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24003BK\"></sup>put in charge of his household to give them their food at the proper time?</span>",
			"46": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>Blessed is that slave whom his master finds so doing when he comes.</span>",
			"47": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>Truly I say to you that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24005BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24005BL\"></sup>he will put him in charge of all his possessions.</span>",
			"48": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>But if that evil slave says in his heart, ‘My master is not coming for a long time,’</span>",
			"49": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>and begins to beat his fellow slaves and eat and drink with drunkards;</span>",
			"50": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>the master of that slave will come on a day when he does not expect <i>him</i> and at an hour which he does not know,</span>",
			"51": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>and will cut him in pieces and assign him a place with the hypocrites; in that place there will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24009BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24009BM\"></sup>weeping and gnashing of teeth.</span>"
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<span class=\"woj\"><span class=\"chapternum\">25 </span>“Then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24010A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24010A\"></sup>the kingdom of heaven will be comparable to ten virgins, who took their <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24010B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24010B\"></sup>lamps and went out to meet the bridegroom.</span>",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Five of them were foolish, and five were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24011C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24011C\"></sup>prudent.</span>",
			"3": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For when the foolish took their lamps, they took no oil with them,</span>",
			"4": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>but the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24013D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24013D\"></sup>prudent took oil in flasks along with their lamps.</span>",
			"5": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Now while the bridegroom was delaying, they all got drowsy and <i>began</i> to sleep.</span>",
			"6": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>But at midnight there was a shout, ‘Behold, the bridegroom! Come out to meet <i>him</i>.’</span>",
			"7": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Then all those virgins rose and trimmed their lamps.</span>",
			"8": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>The foolish said to the prudent, ‘Give us some of your oil, for our lamps are going out.’</span>",
			"9": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>But the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24018E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24018E\"></sup>prudent answered, ‘No, there will not be enough for us and you <i>too</i>; go instead to the dealers and buy <i>some</i> for yourselves.’</span>",
			"10": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>And while they were going away to make the purchase, the bridegroom came, and those who were <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24019F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24019F\"></sup>ready went in with him to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24019G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24019G\"></sup>the wedding feast; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24019H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24019H\"></sup>the door was shut.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Later the other virgins also came, saying, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24020I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24020I\"></sup>Lord, lord, open up for us.’</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>But he answered, ‘Truly I say to you, I do not know you.’</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24022J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24022J\"></sup>Be on the alert then, for you do not know the day nor the hour.</span>",
			"14": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24023K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24023K\"></sup>For <i>it is</i> just like a man <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24023L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24023L\"></sup><i>about</i> to go on a journey, who called his own slaves and entrusted his possessions to them.</span>",
			"15": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>To one he gave five <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24024M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24024M\"></sup>talents, to another, two, and to another, one, each according to his own ability; and he <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24024N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24024N\"></sup>went on his journey.</span>",
			"16": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Immediately the one who had received the five <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24025O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24025O\"></sup>talents went and traded with them, and gained five more talents.</span>",
			"17": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>In the same manner the one who <i>had received</i> the two <i>talents</i> gained two more.</span>",
			"18": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>But he who received the one <i>talent</i> went away, and dug <i>a hole</i> in the ground and hid his master’s money.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>“Now after a long time the master of those slaves *came and *<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24028P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24028P\"></sup>settled accounts with them.</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>The one who had received the five <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24029Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24029Q\"></sup>talents came up and brought five more talents, saying, ‘Master, you entrusted five talents to me. See, I have gained five more talents.’</span>",
			"21": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>His master said to him, ‘Well done, good and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24030R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24030R\"></sup>faithful slave. You were faithful with a few things, I will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24030S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24030S\"></sup>put you in charge of many things; enter into the joy of your master.’</span>",
			"22": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>“Also the one who <i>had received</i> the two <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24031T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24031T\"></sup>talents came up and said, ‘Master, you entrusted two talents to me. See, I have gained two more talents.’</span>",
			"23": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>His master said to him, ‘Well done, good and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24032U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24032U\"></sup>faithful slave. You were faithful with a few things, I will put you in charge of many things; enter into the joy of your master.’</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>“And the one also who had received the one <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24033V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24033V\"></sup>talent came up and said, ‘Master, I knew you to be a hard man, reaping where you did not sow and gathering where you scattered no <i>seed</i>.</span>",
			"25": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And I was afraid, and went away and hid your talent in the ground. See, you have what is yours.’</span>",
			"26": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>“But his master answered and said to him, ‘You wicked, lazy slave, you knew that I reap where I did not sow and gather where I scattered no <i>seed</i>.</span>",
			"27": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>Then you ought to have put my money in the bank, and on my arrival I would have received my <i>money</i> back with interest.</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>Therefore take away the talent from him, and give it to the one who has the ten talents.’</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24038W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24038W\"></sup>For to everyone who has, <i>more</i> shall be given, and he will have an abundance; but from the one who does not have, even what he does have shall be taken away.</span>",
			"30": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup>Throw out the worthless slave into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24039X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24039X\"></sup>the outer darkness; in that place there will be weeping and gnashing of teeth.</span>",
			"31": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>“But when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24040Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24040Y\"></sup>the Son of Man comes in His glory, and all the angels with Him, then <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24040Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24040Z\"></sup>He will sit on His glorious throne.</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>All the nations will be <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24041AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24041AA\"></sup>gathered before Him; and He will separate them from one another, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24041AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24041AB\"></sup>as the shepherd separates the sheep from the goats;</span>",
			"33": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>and He will put the sheep <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24042AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24042AC\"></sup>on His right, and the goats <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24042AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24042AD\"></sup>on the left.</span>",
			"34": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>“Then the King will say to those on His right, ‘Come, you who are blessed of My Father, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24043AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24043AE\"></sup>inherit the kingdom prepared for you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24043AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24043AF\"></sup>from the foundation of the world.</span>",
			"35": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>For <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24044AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24044AG\"></sup>I was hungry, and you gave Me <i>something</i> to eat; I was thirsty, and you gave Me <i>something</i> to drink; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24044AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24044AH\"></sup>I was a stranger, and you invited Me in;</span>",
			"36": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24045AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24045AI\"></sup>naked, and you clothed Me; I was sick, and you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24045AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24045AJ\"></sup>visited Me; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24045AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24045AK\"></sup>I was in prison, and you came to Me.’</span>",
			"37": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>Then the righteous will answer Him, ‘Lord, when did we see You hungry, and feed You, or thirsty, and give You <i>something</i> to drink?</span>",
			"38": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>And when did we see You a stranger, and invite You in, or naked, and clothe You?</span>",
			"39": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>When did we see You sick, or in prison, and come to You?’</span>",
			"40": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24049AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24049AL\"></sup>The King will answer and say to them, ‘Truly I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24049AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24049AM\"></sup>to the extent that you did it to one of these brothers of Mine, <i>even</i> the least <i>of them</i>, you did it to Me.’</span>",
			"41": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>“Then He will also say to those on His left, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24050AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24050AN\"></sup>Depart from Me, accursed ones, into the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24050AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24050AO\"></sup>eternal fire which has been prepared for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24050AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24050AP\"></sup>the devil and his angels;</span>",
			"42": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>for I was hungry, and you gave Me <i>nothing</i> to eat; I was thirsty, and you gave Me nothing to drink;</span>",
			"43": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>I was a stranger, and you did not invite Me in; naked, and you did not clothe Me; sick, and in prison, and you did not visit Me.’</span>",
			"44": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>Then they themselves also will answer, ‘Lord, when did we see You hungry, or thirsty, or a stranger, or naked, or sick, or in prison, and did not take care of You?’</span>",
			"45": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>Then He will answer them, ‘Truly I say to you, to the extent that you did not do it to one of the least of these, you did not do it to Me.’</span>",
			"46": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>These will go away into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24055AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24055AQ\"></sup>eternal punishment, but the righteous into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24055AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24055AR\"></sup>eternal life.”</span>"
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">26 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24056A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24056A\"></sup>When Jesus had finished all these words, He said to His disciples,",
			"2": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24057B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24057B\"></sup>You know that after two days <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24057C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24057C\"></sup>the Passover is coming, and the Son of Man is <i>to be</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24057D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24057D\"></sup>handed over for crucifixion.”</span>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24058E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24058E\"></sup>Then the chief priests and the elders of the people were gathered together in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24058F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24058F\"></sup>the court of the high priest, named <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24058G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24058G\"></sup>Caiaphas;",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>and they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24059H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24059H\"></sup>plotted together to seize Jesus by stealth and kill Him.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>But they were saying, “Not during the festival, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24060I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24060I\"></sup>otherwise a riot might occur among the people.”",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24061J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24061J\"></sup>Now when Jesus was in <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24061K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24061K\"></sup>Bethany, at the home of Simon the leper,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24062L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24062L\"></sup>a woman came to Him with an alabaster vial of very costly perfume, and she poured it on His head as He reclined <i>at the table</i>.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But the disciples were indignant when they saw <i>this</i>, and said, “Why this waste?",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For this <i>perfume</i> might have been sold for a high price and <i>the money</i> given to the poor.”",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>But Jesus, aware of this, said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Why do you bother the woman? For she has done a good deed to Me.</span>",
			"11": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>For you always have <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24066M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24066M\"></sup>the poor with you; but you do not always have Me.</span>",
			"12": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>For when she poured this perfume on My body, she did it <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24067N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24067N\"></sup>to prepare Me for burial.</span>",
			"13": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Truly I say to you, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24068O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24068O\"></sup>wherever this gospel is preached in the whole world, what this woman has done will also be spoken of in memory of her.”</span>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24069P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24069P\"></sup>Then one of the twelve, named <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24069Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24069Q\"></sup>Judas Iscariot, went to the chief priests",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>and said, “What are you willing to give me to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24070R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24070R\"></sup>betray Him to you?” And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24070S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24070S\"></sup>they weighed out thirty pieces of silver to him.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>From then on he <i>began</i> looking for a good opportunity to betray Jesus.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24072T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24072T\"></sup>Now on the first <i>day</i> of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24072U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24072U\"></sup>Unleavened Bread the disciples came to Jesus and asked, “Where do You want us to prepare for You to eat the Passover?”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And He said, <span class=\"woj\">“Go into the city to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24073V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24073V\"></sup>a certain man, and say to him, ‘The Teacher says, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24073W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24073W\"></sup>My time is near; I <i>am to</i> keep the Passover at your house with My disciples.”’”</span>",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>The disciples did as Jesus had directed them; and they prepared the Passover.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24075X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24075X\"></sup>Now when evening came, Jesus was reclining <i>at the table</i> with the twelve disciples.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>As they were eating, He said, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24076Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24076Y\"></sup>Truly I say to you that one of you will betray Me.”</span>",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Being deeply grieved, they each one began to say to Him, “Surely not I, Lord?”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And He answered, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24078Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24078Z\"></sup>He who dipped his hand with Me in the bowl is the one who will betray Me.</span>",
			"24": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>The Son of Man <i>is to</i> go, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24079AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24079AA\"></sup>just as it is written of Him; but woe to that man by whom the Son of Man is betrayed! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24079AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24079AB\"></sup>It would have been good for that man if he had not been born.”</span>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24080AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24080AC\"></sup>Judas, who was betraying Him, said, “Surely it is not I, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24080AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24080AD\"></sup>Rabbi?” Jesus *said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24080AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24080AE\"></sup>You have said <i>it</i> yourself.”</span>",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24081AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24081AF\"></sup>While they were eating, Jesus took <i>some</i> bread, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24081AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24081AG\"></sup>after a blessing, He broke <i>it</i> and gave <i>it</i> to the disciples, and said, <span class=\"woj\">“Take, eat; this is My body.”</span>",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>And when He had taken a cup and given thanks, He gave <i>it</i> to them, saying, <span class=\"woj\">“Drink from it, all of you;</span>",
			"28": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24083AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24083AH\"></sup>this is My blood of the covenant, which is poured out for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24083AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24083AI\"></sup>many for forgiveness of sins.</span>",
			"29": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>But I say to you, I will not drink of this fruit of the vine from now on until that day when I drink it new with you in My Father’s kingdom.”</span>",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24085AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24085AJ\"></sup>After singing a hymn, they went out to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24085AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24085AK\"></sup>the Mount of Olives.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup>Then Jesus *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“You will all <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24086AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24086AL\"></sup>fall away because of Me this night, for it is written, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24086AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24086AM\"></sup>I <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">will strike down the shepherd, and the sheep of the flock shall be</span> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24086AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24086AN\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">scattered</span>.’</span>",
			"32": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup>But after I have been raised, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24087AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24087AO\"></sup>I will go ahead of you to Galilee.”</span>",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup>But Peter said to Him, “<i>Even</i> though all may fall away because of You, I will never fall away.”",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup>Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24089AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24089AP\"></sup>Truly I say to you that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24089AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24089AQ\"></sup>this <i>very</i> night, before a rooster crows, you will deny Me three times.”</span>",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>Peter *said to Him, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24090AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24090AR\"></sup>Even if I have to die with You, I will not deny You.” All the disciples said the same thing too.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24091AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24091AS\"></sup>Then Jesus *came with them to a place called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24091AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24091AT\"></sup>Gethsemane, and *said to His disciples, <span class=\"woj\">“Sit here while I go over there and pray.”</span>",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>And He took with Him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24092AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24092AU\"></sup>Peter and the two sons of Zebedee, and began to be grieved and distressed.",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>Then He *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24093AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24093AV\"></sup>My soul is deeply grieved, to the point of death; remain here and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24093AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24093AW\"></sup>keep watch with Me.”</span>",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>And He went a little beyond <i>them</i>, and fell on His face and prayed, saying, <span class=\"woj\">“My Father, if it is possible, let <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24094AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24094AX\"></sup>this cup pass from Me; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24094AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24094AY\"></sup>yet not as I will, but as You will.”</span>",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>And He *came to the disciples and *found them sleeping, and *said to Peter, <span class=\"woj\">“So, you <i>men</i> could not <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24095AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24095AZ\"></sup>keep watch with Me for one hour?</span>",
			"41": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24096BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24096BA\"></sup>Keep watching and praying that you may not enter into temptation; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24096BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24096BB\"></sup>the spirit is willing, but the flesh is weak.”</span>",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>He went away again a second time and prayed, saying, <span class=\"woj\">“My Father, if this <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24097BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24097BC\"></sup>cannot pass away unless I drink it, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24097BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24097BD\"></sup>Your will be done.”</span>",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup>Again He came and found them sleeping, for their eyes were heavy.",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup>And He left them again, and went away and prayed a third time, saying the same thing once more.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup>Then He *came to the disciples and *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“Are you still sleeping and resting? Behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24100BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24100BE\"></sup>the hour is at hand and the Son of Man is being betrayed into the hands of sinners.</span>",
			"46": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>Get up, let us be going; behold, the one who betrays Me is at hand!”</span>",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24102BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24102BF\"></sup>While He was still speaking, behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24102BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24102BG\"></sup>Judas, one of the twelve, came up accompanied by a large crowd with swords and clubs, <i>who came</i> from the chief priests and elders of the people.",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup>Now he who was betraying Him gave them a sign, saying, “Whomever I kiss, He is the one; seize Him.”",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>Immediately Judas went to Jesus and said, “Hail, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24104BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24104BH\"></sup>Rabbi!” and kissed Him.",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>And Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24105BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24105BI\"></sup>Friend, <i>do</i> what you have come for.”</span> Then they came and laid hands on Jesus and seized Him.",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup>And behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24106BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24106BJ\"></sup>one of those who were with Jesus reached and drew out his <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24106BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24106BK\"></sup>sword, and struck the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24106BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24106BL\"></sup>slave of the high priest and cut off his ear.",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>Then Jesus *said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“Put your sword back into its place; for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24107BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24107BM\"></sup>all those who take up the sword shall perish by the sword.</span>",
			"53": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>Or do you think that I cannot appeal to My Father, and He will at once put at My disposal more than twelve <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24108BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24108BN\"></sup>legions of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24108BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24108BO\"></sup>angels?</span>",
			"54": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup>How then will <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24109BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24109BP\"></sup>the Scriptures be fulfilled, <i>which say</i> that it must happen this way?”</span>",
			"55": "<sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup>At that time Jesus said to the crowds, <span class=\"woj\">“Have you come out with swords and clubs to arrest Me as <i>you would</i> against a robber? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24110BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24110BQ\"></sup>Every day I used to sit in the temple teaching and you did not seize Me.</span>",
			"56": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup>But all this has taken place to fulfill <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24111BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24111BR\"></sup>the Scriptures of the prophets.”</span> Then all the disciples left Him and fled.",
			"57": "<sup class=\"versenum\">57 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24112BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24112BS\"></sup>Those who had seized Jesus led Him away to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24112BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24112BT\"></sup>Caiaphas, the high priest, where the scribes and the elders were gathered together.",
			"58": "<sup class=\"versenum\">58 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24113BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24113BU\"></sup>Peter was following Him at a distance as far as the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24113BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24113BV\"></sup>courtyard of the high priest, and entered in, and sat down with the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24113BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24113BW\"></sup>officers to see the outcome.",
			"59": "<sup class=\"versenum\">59 </sup>Now the chief priests and the whole <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24114BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24114BX\"></sup>Council kept trying to obtain false testimony against Jesus, so that they might put Him to death.",
			"60": "<sup class=\"versenum\">60 </sup>They did not find <i>any</i>, even though many false witnesses came forward. But later on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24115BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24115BY\"></sup>two came forward,",
			"61": "<sup class=\"versenum\">61 </sup>and said, “This man stated, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24116BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24116BZ\"></sup>I am able to destroy the temple of God and to rebuild it in three days.’”",
			"62": "<sup class=\"versenum\">62 </sup>The high priest stood up and said to Him, “Do You not answer? What is it that these men are testifying against You?”",
			"63": "<sup class=\"versenum\">63 </sup>But <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24118CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24118CA\"></sup>Jesus kept silent. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24118CB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CB&quot;&gt;CB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24118CB\"></sup>And the high priest said to Him, “I <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24118CC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CC&quot;&gt;CC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24118CC\"></sup>adjure You by <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24118CD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CD&quot;&gt;CD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24118CD\"></sup>the living God, that You tell us whether You are the Christ, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24118CE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CE&quot;&gt;CE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24118CE\"></sup>the Son of God.”",
			"64": "<sup class=\"versenum\">64 </sup>Jesus *said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24119CF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CF&quot;&gt;CF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24119CF\"></sup>You have said it <i>yourself</i>; nevertheless I tell you, hereafter you will see <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24119CG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CG&quot;&gt;CG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24119CG\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">the Son of Man sitting at the right hand of Power</span>, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24119CH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CH&quot;&gt;CH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24119CH\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">coming on the clouds of heaven</span>.”</span>",
			"65": "<sup class=\"versenum\">65 </sup>Then the high priest <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24120CI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CI&quot;&gt;CI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24120CI\"></sup>tore his robes and said, “He has blasphemed! What further need do we have of witnesses? Behold, you have now heard the blasphemy;",
			"66": "<sup class=\"versenum\">66 </sup>what do you think?” They answered, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24121CJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CJ&quot;&gt;CJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24121CJ\"></sup>He deserves death!”",
			"67": "<sup class=\"versenum\">67 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24122CK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CK&quot;&gt;CK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24122CK\"></sup>Then they <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24122CL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CL&quot;&gt;CL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24122CL\"></sup>spat in His face and beat Him with their fists; and others slapped Him,",
			"68": "<sup class=\"versenum\">68 </sup>and said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24123CM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CM&quot;&gt;CM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24123CM\"></sup>Prophesy to us, You Christ; who is the one who hit You?”",
			"69": "<sup class=\"versenum\">69 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24124CN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CN&quot;&gt;CN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24124CN\"></sup>Now Peter was sitting outside in the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24124CO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CO&quot;&gt;CO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24124CO\"></sup>courtyard, and a servant-girl came to him and said, “You too were with Jesus the Galilean.”",
			"70": "<sup class=\"versenum\">70 </sup>But he denied <i>it</i> before them all, saying, “I do not know what you are talking about.”",
			"71": "<sup class=\"versenum\">71 </sup>When he had gone out to the gateway, another <i>servant-girl</i> saw him and *said to those who were there, “This man was with Jesus of Nazareth.”",
			"72": "<sup class=\"versenum\">72 </sup>And again he denied <i>it</i> with an oath, “I do not know the man.”",
			"73": "<sup class=\"versenum\">73 </sup>A little later the bystanders came up and said to Peter, “Surely you too are <i>one</i> of them; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24128CP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CP&quot;&gt;CP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24128CP\"></sup>for even the way you talk gives you away.”",
			"74": "<sup class=\"versenum\">74 </sup>Then he began to curse and swear, “I do not know the man!” And immediately a rooster crowed.",
			"75": "<sup class=\"versenum\">75 </sup>And Peter remembered the word which Jesus had said, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24130CQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CQ&quot;&gt;CQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24130CQ\"></sup>Before a rooster crows, you will deny Me three times.”</span> And he went out and wept bitterly."
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">27 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24131A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24131A\"></sup>Now when morning came, all the chief priests and the elders of the people conferred together against Jesus to put Him to death;",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>and they bound Him, and led Him away and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24132B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24132B\"></sup>delivered Him to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24132C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24132C\"></sup>Pilate the governor.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>Then when <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24133D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24133D\"></sup>Judas, who had betrayed Him, saw that He had been condemned, he felt remorse and returned <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24133E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24133E\"></sup>the thirty pieces of silver to the chief priests and elders,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>saying, “I have sinned by betraying innocent blood.” But they said, “What is that to us? <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24134F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24134F\"></sup>See <i>to that</i> yourself!”",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>And he threw the pieces of silver into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24135G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24135G\"></sup>the temple sanctuary and departed; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24135H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24135H\"></sup>he went away and hanged himself.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>The chief priests took the pieces of silver and said, “It is not lawful to put them into the temple treasury, since it is the price of blood.”",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>And they conferred together and with the money bought the Potter’s Field as a burial place for strangers.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24138I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24138I\"></sup>For this reason that field has been called the Field of Blood to this day.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Then that which was spoken through Jeremiah the prophet was fulfilled: “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24139J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24139J\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">And</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">they took the thirty pieces of silver, the price of the one whose price had been set</span> by the sons of Israel;",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24140K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24140K\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">and</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">they gave them for the Potter’s Field, as the Lord directed me</span>.”",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24141L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24141L\"></sup>Now Jesus stood before the governor, and the governor questioned Him, saying, “Are You the <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24141M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24141M\"></sup>King of the Jews?” And Jesus said to him, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24141N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24141N\"></sup><i>It is as</i> you say.”</span>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And while He was being accused by the chief priests and elders, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24142O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24142O\"></sup>He did not answer.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Then Pilate *said to Him, “Do You not hear how many things they testify against You?”",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24144P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24144P\"></sup>He did not answer him with regard to even a <i>single</i> charge, so the governor was quite amazed.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24145Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24145Q\"></sup>Now at <i>the</i> feast the governor was accustomed to release for the people <i>any</i> one prisoner whom they wanted.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>At that time they were holding a notorious prisoner, called Barabbas.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>So when the people gathered together, Pilate said to them, “Whom do you want me to release for you? Barabbas, or Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24147R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24147R\"></sup>who is called Christ?”",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>For he knew that because of envy they had handed Him over.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24149S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24149S\"></sup>While he was sitting on the judgment seat, his wife sent him <i>a message</i>, saying, “Have nothing to do with that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24149T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24149T\"></sup>righteous Man; for last night I suffered greatly <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24149U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24149U\"></sup>in a dream because of Him.”",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>But the chief priests and the elders persuaded the crowds to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24150V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24150V\"></sup>ask for Barabbas and to put Jesus to death.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>But the governor said to them, “Which of the two do you want me to release for you?” And they said, “Barabbas.”",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Pilate *said to them, “Then what shall I do with Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24152W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24152W\"></sup>who is called Christ?” They all *said, “Crucify Him!”",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>And he said, “Why, what evil has He done?” But they kept shouting all the more, saying, “Crucify Him!”",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>When Pilate saw that he was accomplishing nothing, but rather that <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24154X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24154X\"></sup>a riot was starting, he took water and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24154Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24154Y\"></sup>washed his hands in front of the crowd, saying, “I am innocent of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24154Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24154Z\"></sup>this Man’s blood; <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24154AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24154AA\"></sup>see <i>to that</i> yourselves.”",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>And all the people said, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24155AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24155AB\"></sup>His blood shall be on us and on our children!”",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>Then he released Barabbas for them; but after having Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24156AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24156AC\"></sup>scourged, he handed Him over to be crucified.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24157AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24157AD\"></sup>Then the soldiers of the governor took Jesus into <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24157AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24157AE\"></sup>the Praetorium and gathered the whole <i>Roman</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24157AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24157AF\"></sup>cohort around Him.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>They stripped Him and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24158AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24158AG\"></sup>put a scarlet robe on Him.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24159AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24159AH\"></sup>And after twisting together a crown of thorns, they put it on His head, and a reed in His right hand; and they knelt down before Him and mocked Him, saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24159AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24159AI\"></sup>Hail, King of the Jews!”",
			"30": "<sup class=\"versenum\">30 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24160AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24160AJ\"></sup>They spat on Him, and took the reed and <i>began</i> to beat Him on the head.",
			"31": "<sup class=\"versenum\">31 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24161AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24161AK\"></sup>After they had mocked Him, they took the <i>scarlet</i> robe off Him and put His <i>own</i> garments back on Him, and led Him away to crucify Him.",
			"32": "<sup class=\"versenum\">32 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24162AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24162AL\"></sup>As they were coming out, they found a man of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24162AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24162AM\"></sup>Cyrene named Simon, whom they pressed into service to bear His cross.",
			"33": "<sup class=\"versenum\">33 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24163AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24163AN\"></sup>And when they came to a place called <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24163AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24163AO\"></sup>Golgotha, which means Place of a Skull,",
			"34": "<sup class=\"versenum\">34 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24164AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24164AP\"></sup>they gave Him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24164AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24164AQ\"></sup>wine to drink mixed with gall; and after tasting <i>it</i>, He was unwilling to drink.",
			"35": "<sup class=\"versenum\">35 </sup>And when they had crucified Him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24165AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24165AR\"></sup>they divided up His garments among themselves by casting lots.",
			"36": "<sup class=\"versenum\">36 </sup>And sitting down, they <i>began</i> to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24166AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24166AS\"></sup>keep watch over Him there.",
			"37": "<sup class=\"versenum\">37 </sup>And above His head they put up the charge against Him which read, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24167AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24167AT\"></sup>THIS IS JESUS THE KING OF THE JEWS.”",
			"38": "<sup class=\"versenum\">38 </sup>At that time two robbers *were crucified with Him, one on the right and one on the left.",
			"39": "<sup class=\"versenum\">39 </sup>And those passing by were hurling abuse at Him, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24169AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24169AU\"></sup>wagging their heads",
			"40": "<sup class=\"versenum\">40 </sup>and saying, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24170AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24170AV\"></sup>You who <i>are going to</i> destroy the temple and rebuild it in three days, save Yourself! <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24170AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24170AW\"></sup>If You are the Son of God, come down from the cross.”",
			"41": "<sup class=\"versenum\">41 </sup>In the same way the chief priests also, along with the scribes and elders, were mocking <i>Him</i> and saying,",
			"42": "<sup class=\"versenum\">42 </sup>“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24172AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24172AX\"></sup>He saved others; He cannot save Himself. <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24172AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24172AY\"></sup>He is the King of Israel; let Him now come down from the cross, and we will believe in Him.",
			"43": "<sup class=\"versenum\">43 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24173AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24173AZ\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">He trusts in God; let God rescue</span> <i>Him</i> now, <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">if He</span> <span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">delights in Him</span>; for He said, ‘I am the Son of God.’”",
			"44": "<sup class=\"versenum\">44 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24174BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24174BA\"></sup>The robbers who had been crucified with Him were also insulting Him with the same words.",
			"45": "<sup class=\"versenum\">45 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24175BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24175BB\"></sup>Now from the sixth hour darkness fell upon all the land until the ninth hour.",
			"46": "<sup class=\"versenum\">46 </sup>About the ninth hour Jesus cried out with a loud voice, saying, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24176BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24176BC\"></sup><span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">Eli, Eli, lama sabachthani</span>?”</span> that is, <span class=\"woj\">“<span style=\"font-variant: small-caps\" class=\"small-caps\">My God, My God, why have You forsaken Me</span>?”</span>",
			"47": "<sup class=\"versenum\">47 </sup>And some of those who were standing there, when they heard it, <i>began</i> saying, “This man is calling for Elijah.”",
			"48": "<sup class=\"versenum\">48 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24178BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24178BD\"></sup>Immediately one of them ran, and taking a sponge, he filled it with sour wine and put it on a reed, and gave Him a drink.",
			"49": "<sup class=\"versenum\">49 </sup>But the rest <i>of them</i> said, “Let us see whether Elijah will come to save Him.”",
			"50": "<sup class=\"versenum\">50 </sup>And Jesus <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24180BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24180BE\"></sup>cried out again with a loud voice, and yielded up His spirit.",
			"51": "<sup class=\"versenum\">51 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24181BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24181BF\"></sup>And behold, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24181BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24181BG\"></sup>the veil of the temple was torn in two from top to bottom; and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24181BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24181BH\"></sup>the earth shook and the rocks were split.",
			"52": "<sup class=\"versenum\">52 </sup>The tombs were opened, and many bodies of the saints who had <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24182BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24182BI\"></sup>fallen asleep were raised;",
			"53": "<sup class=\"versenum\">53 </sup>and coming out of the tombs after His resurrection they entered <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24183BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24183BJ\"></sup>the holy city and appeared to many.",
			"54": "<sup class=\"versenum\">54 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24184BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24184BK\"></sup>Now the centurion, and those who were with him <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24184BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24184BL\"></sup>keeping guard over Jesus, when they saw <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24184BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24184BM\"></sup>the earthquake and the things that were happening, became very frightened and said, “Truly this was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24184BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24184BN\"></sup>the Son of God!”",
			"55": "<sup class=\"versenum\">55 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24185BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24185BO\"></sup>Many women were there looking on from a distance, who had followed Jesus from Galilee while <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24185BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24185BP\"></sup>ministering to Him.",
			"56": "<sup class=\"versenum\">56 </sup>Among them was <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24186BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24186BQ\"></sup>Mary Magdalene, and Mary the mother of James and Joseph, and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24186BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24186BR\"></sup>the mother of the sons of Zebedee.",
			"57": "<sup class=\"versenum\">57 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24187BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24187BS\"></sup>When it was evening, there came a rich man from Arimathea, named Joseph, who himself had also become a disciple of Jesus.",
			"58": "<sup class=\"versenum\">58 </sup>This man went to Pilate and asked for the body of Jesus. Then Pilate ordered it to be given <i>to him</i>.",
			"59": "<sup class=\"versenum\">59 </sup>And Joseph took the body and wrapped it in a clean linen cloth,",
			"60": "<sup class=\"versenum\">60 </sup>and laid it in his own new tomb, which he had hewn out in the rock; and he rolled <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24190BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24190BT\"></sup>a large stone against the entrance of the tomb and went away.",
			"61": "<sup class=\"versenum\">61 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24191BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24191BU\"></sup>Mary Magdalene was there, and the other Mary, sitting opposite the grave.",
			"62": "<sup class=\"versenum\">62 </sup>Now on the next day, the day after <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24192BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24192BV\"></sup>the preparation, the chief priests and the Pharisees gathered together with Pilate,",
			"63": "<sup class=\"versenum\">63 </sup>and said, “Sir, we remember that when He was still alive that deceiver said, ‘<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24193BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24193BW\"></sup>After three days I <i>am to</i> rise again.’",
			"64": "<sup class=\"versenum\">64 </sup>Therefore, give orders for the grave to be made secure until the third day, otherwise His disciples may come and steal Him away and say to the people, ‘He has risen from the dead,’ and the last deception will be worse than the first.”",
			"65": "<sup class=\"versenum\">65 </sup>Pilate said to them, “You have a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24195BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24195BX\"></sup>guard; go, make it <i>as</i> secure as you know how.”",
			"66": "<sup class=\"versenum\">66 </sup>And they went and made the grave secure, and along with <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24196BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24196BY\"></sup>the guard they set a <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24196BZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BZ&quot;&gt;BZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24196BZ\"></sup>seal on <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24196CA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference CA&quot;&gt;CA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24196CA\"></sup>the stone."
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">28 </span><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24197A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24197A\"></sup>Now after the Sabbath, as it began to dawn toward the first <i>day</i> of the week, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24197B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24197B\"></sup>Mary Magdalene and the other Mary came to look at the grave.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>And behold, a severe earthquake had occurred, for <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24198C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24198C\"></sup>an angel of the Lord descended from heaven and came and rolled away <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24198D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24198D\"></sup>the stone and sat upon it.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24199E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24199E\"></sup>his appearance was like lightning, and his clothing as white as snow.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>The guards shook for fear of him and became like dead men.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>The angel said to the women, “<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24201F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24201F\"></sup>Do not be afraid; for I know that you are looking for Jesus who has been crucified.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>He is not here, for He has risen, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24202G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24202G\"></sup>just as He said. Come, see the place where He was lying.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Go quickly and tell His disciples that He has risen from the dead; and behold, He is going ahead of you <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24203H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24203H\"></sup>into Galilee, there you will see Him; behold, I have told you.”",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>And they left the tomb quickly with fear and great joy and ran to report it to His disciples.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>And behold, Jesus met them and greeted them. And they came up and took hold of His feet and worshiped Him.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>Then Jesus *said to them, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24206I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24206I\"></sup>Do not be afraid; go and take word to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24206J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24206J\"></sup>My brethren to leave <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24206K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24206K\"></sup>for Galilee, and there they will see Me.”</span>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Now while they were on their way, some of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24207L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24207L\"></sup>the guard came into the city and reported to the chief priests all that had happened.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>And when they had assembled with the elders and consulted together, they gave a large sum of money to the soldiers,",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>and said, “You are to say, ‘His disciples came by night and stole Him away while we were asleep.’",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And if this should come to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24210M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24210M\"></sup>the governor’s ears, we will win him over and keep you out of trouble.”",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And they took the money and did as they had been instructed; and this story was widely <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24211N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24211N\"></sup>spread among the Jews, <i>and is</i> <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24211O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24211O\"></sup>to this day.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>But the eleven disciples proceeded <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24212P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24212P\"></sup>to Galilee, to the mountain which Jesus had designated.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>When they saw Him, they worshiped <i>Him</i>; but <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24213Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24213Q\"></sup>some were doubtful.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And Jesus came up and spoke to them, saying, <span class=\"woj\">“<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24214R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24214R\"></sup>All authority has been given to Me in heaven and on earth.</span>",
			"19": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup><sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24215S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24215S\"></sup>Go therefore and <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24215T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24215T\"></sup>make disciples of <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24215U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24215U\"></sup>all the nations, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24215V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24215V\"></sup>baptizing them in the name of the Father and the Son and the Holy Spirit,</span>",
			"20": "<span class=\"woj\"><sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>teaching them to observe all that I commanded you; and lo, <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24216W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24216W\"></sup>I am with you always, even to <sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NASB-24216X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NASB-24216X\"></sup>the end of the age.”</span>"
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;